04%20to%202009%2C%20drew%20a%20parallel%20between%20the%20election%20guarantees%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20welfare%20measures%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20talked%20about%20relief%20to%20common%20people%2C%20we%20didn't%20have%20elections%20in%20our%20mind.%20We%20will%20be%20happy%20if%20Shivraj%20Chouhan%20announces%20gas%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500.%20And%20I%20have%20heard%20he%20is%20going%20to%20make%20that%20announcement.%20After%20our%20announcements%2C%20he%20is%20thinking%20of%20cylinders%20and%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20said%20we%20would%20give%20Rs%201500%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20give%20Rs%202%2C000.%20If%20they%20do%20it%2C%20it%20fulfils%20our%20goal%20as%20our%20goal%20is%20not%20votes%2C%20but%20people's%20welfare%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20high%20on%20its%20Karnataka%20win%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20%26quot%3Belection%20guarantees%26quot%3B%20for%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20similar%20to%20the%20ones%20it%20implemented%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress'%20promise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Gas%20cylinder%3A%20Rs%20500%3B%201%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20every%20woman%3B%20Electricity%3A%20100%20units%20waived%2C%20200%20units%20halved%3B%20farm%20loan%20waived%3B%20old%20pension%20scheme%20will%20be%20applicable.%20We%20kept%20our%20promise%20in%20Karnataka%20-%20now%20we%20will%20keep%20it%20in%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20had%20said%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20in%20the%20central%20state%20since%202003%2C%20except%20for%20a%20break%20between%20December%202018%20and%20March%202020%20when%20the%20state%20had%20a%20Congress%20government%20under%20Kamal%20Nath.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692619860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkcdiane_kamal-na