ould%20help%20achieve%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMaersk%20launched%20a%20methanol-powered%20vessel%20last%20month%2C%20and%20Cargill%20announced%20a%20wind-powered%20one%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EShipping%20is%20an%20increasingly%20polluting%20industry%2C%20responsible%20for%203%25%20of%20the%20world's%20greenhouse%20gases%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fresearch-and-innovation%2Fen%2Fhorizon-magazine%2Femissions-free-sailing-full-steam-ahead-ocean-going-shipping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UN's%20International%20Maritime%20Organization%20announced%20plans%20in%202020%20to%20reduce%20the%20sector's%20emissions%20by%2050%25%20by%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20two%20cargo%20ships%20that%20have%20launched%20in%20the%20last%20five%20weeks%20are%20set%20to%20help%20achieve%20that%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDanish%20shipping%20giant%20Maersk%20originally%20planned%20to%20operate%20the%20world's%20first%20carbon-neutral%20liner%20vessel%20by%202030%2C%20but%20brought%20its%20target%20forward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maersk.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021%2F02%2F17%2Fmaersk-first-carbon-neutral-liner-vessel-by-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eby%20seven%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20first%20ship%20fueled%20by%20green%20methanol%20began%20its%20maiden%20voyage%20on%20July%2017%20from%20South%20Korea%20to%20Denmark%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaritime-executive.com%2Farticle%2Ffirst-green-methanol-fueled-boxship-starts-maiden-voyage-for-maersk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Maritime%20Executive%3C%2Fa%3E%20first%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20visualisation%20of%20a%20Maersk%20'green%20fuel'%20cargo%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e35175bd98a600197abe35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%20Maersk%20says%20it%20has%2025%20methanol-enabled%20vessels%20on%20order.%3Cp%3EMaric%20Design%2FMaersk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%2025%20methanol-powered%20ships%20ordered%20by%20Maersk%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscientist.com%2Farticle%2F2388177-first-cargo-ship-powered-by-green-methanol-has-begun-maiden-voyage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Scientist%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20marking%20a%20big%20push%20to%20decarbonize%20the%20shipping%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaersk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.maersk.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023%2F06%2F21%2Fmaersk-to-pioneer-first-container-vessel-conversion-to-methanol-dual-fuel-engine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20vessels%20could%20help%20reach%20its%20target%20of%20a%2050%25%20reduction%20in%20its%20emissions%20per%20transported%20container%20by%202030%20compared%20to%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20Monday%2C%20Cargill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cargill.com%2F2023%2Fcargill-bar-technologies-wind-technology-sets-sail%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20a%20Mitsubishi%20wind-powered%20ship%20it%20has%20chartered%20has%20set%20sail%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pyxis%20Ocean%20was%20retrofitted%20with%20two%20WindWings%2C%20huge%20sails%20designed%20for%20cargo%20ships%20by%20BAR%20technologies%2C%20which%20Cargill%20says%20can%20reduce%20emissions%20by%20up%20to%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20international%20shipping%20is%20to%20achieve%20its%20ambition%20of%20reducing%20CO2%20emissions%2C%20then%20innovation%20must%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Cooper%2C%20CEO%20of%20BAR%20technologies.%20%26quot%3BWind%20is%20a%20near%20marginal%20cost-free%20fuel%20and%20the%20opportunity%20for%20reducing%20emissions%2C%20alongside%20significant%20efficiency%20gains%20in%20vessel%20oper