n%20getting%20the%20abortion%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20Delhi%20Police%20officer%20Sagar%20Singh%20Khalsi%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20was%20a%20local%20guardian...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShortly%20before%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20Khakha%20was%20suspended%20from%20his%20post%20as%20Assistant%20Director%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Department.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKhakha's%20suspension%20was%20confirmed%20hours%20after%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20ripped%20into%20Delhi%20Police%20-%20which%20reports%20to%20the%20union%20government%20controlled%20by%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20-%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20arresting%20him.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20AAP%20said%20the%20'failure%20to%20arrest%20the%20officer%20is%20the%20worst%20part%20of%20this%20case'%20and%20demanded%20Khakha%20be%20prosecuted%20to%20the%20maximum%20extent%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDelhi%20minister%20Atishi%20has%20called%20on%20police%20to%20act%20as%20swiftly%20as%20Kejriwal%20did%20to%20suspend%20Khakha.%20%26quot%3B...a%20shocking%20incident%20as%20this%20accused%20was%20an%20officer%20in%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Department...%20I%20hope%20Delhi%20Police%20will%20do%20the%20proceedings%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEarlier%20today%20police%20detained%20Khakha%20-%20who%20faces%20charges%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20-%20and%20his%20wife.%20Both%20were%20interrogated.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKhakha%20is%20accused%20of%20raping%20the%20minor%20daughter%20of%20his%20friend%20multiple%20times.%20The%20young%20girl%2C%20then%2014%20years%20old%2C%20became%20pregnant%20during%20this%20period%20and%20Khakha's%20wife%20allegedly%20gave%20her%20abortion%20pills%20while%20covering%20for%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rapes%20occurred%20between%20November%202020%20and%20January%202021%20-%20when%20the%20girl%20was%20living%20with%20Khakha%20and%20his%20wife%3B%20this%20was%20after%20her%20father%20died.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rapes%20were%20revealed%20this%20month%20after%20the%20girl%20narrated%20her%20ordeal%20to%20a%20therapist%20at%20Delhi's%20St%20Stephen's%20Hospital%2C%20where%20she%20was%20receiving%20treatment%20for%20panic%20attacks.%20The%20girl%20was%20provided%20therapy%20during%20which%20she%20told%20doctors%20about%20the%20repeated%20sexual%20assault%20she%20faced%20from%20her%20father's%20friend%20-%20someone%20she%20called%20'mama'%20(uncle).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDelhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20chief%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20labelled%20Khakha%20a%20'predator'.%20%26quot%3B...%20if%20the%20one%20whose%20job%20was%20to%20protect%20the%20daughters%20turns%20into%20a%20predator%2C%20then%20where%20will%20the%20girls%20go!%20Must%20be%20arrested%20soon!%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692619740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Ftm4ncqlo_rapist-wife-facebook_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-officer-accused-of-raping-friends-teenage-daughter-arrested-4315446%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Premoday%20Khakha%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20official%20accused%20of%20raping%20a%20teen%20girl%20multiple%20times%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said%20Monday.%20His%20wife%20-%20accused%20of%20giving%20the%20teen%20abortion%20medication%20after%20her%20husband%20impregnated%20her%20-%20has%20also%20been%20arrested.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-officer-accused-of-raping-friends-teenage-daughter-arrested-4315446%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fd