%20The%20Park%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20squad%20for%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20was%20announced%20on%20Monday%20and%20during%20the%20press%20conference%20following%20the%20reveal%2C%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20regarding%20the%20possible%20team%20combinations%20and%20how%20the%20batting%20order%20can%20look%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20first%20match%20of%20the%20competition.%20However%2C%20the%20veteran%20batter%20was%20completely%20unfazed%20by%20the%20queries%20and%20he%20came%20up%20with%20a%20straight%20yet%20hilarious%20answer.%20He%20explained%20that%20most%20slots%20in%20the%20batting%20order%20are%20already%20decided%20with%20No.%204%20and%205%20being%20the%20slots%20where%20some%20flexibility%20is%20possible.%20He%20further%20explained%20that%20youngsters%20will%20be%20shuffled%20in%20different%20positions%20and%20joked%20that%20the%20team%20will%20not%20indulge%20in%20'madness'%20like%20%26quot%3Bsending%20a%20opener%20to%20bat%20at%20No%208%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20openers%20will%20bat%20at%20their%20positions%2C%20same%20with%20the%20number%203%2C%20the%20spot%20is%20fixed%20(for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E%20played%20at%20number%205%20before%20the%20injury%20he%20will%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%20will