or%20London%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20Roblin%20pointed%20out%20that%20Gulf%20states%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20hyping%20arms%20buys%20from%20new%20sources%2C%20including%20Russia%20or%20China%2C%20to%20elicit%20%26quot%3Bjealous%20counteroffers%20from%20their%20'main'%20strategic%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ERyan%20Bohl%2C%20a%20senior%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20analyst%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20said%20Rafales%20could%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Battractive%20option%26quot%3B%20to%20Riyadh%2C%20which%20remembers%20well%20the%20US%20and%20German%20sanctions%20imposed%20on%20it%20after%20the%20assassination%20of%20journalist%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EFrench%20jets%20are%20also%20modern%20and%20built%20by%20a%20NATO%20country%2C%20potentially%20reducing%20issues%20with%20integrating%20the%20jets%20with%20the%20Saudis'%20other%20Western%20aircraft.%20France's%20less%20restrictive%20end-user%20agreements%20%26quot%3Bunderlines%20this%20attractiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ERiyadh's%20non-NATO%20options%20for%20jets%20are%20relatively%20limited%2C%20and%20buying%20Russian%20or%20Chinese%20jets%20would%20likely%20incur%20US%20sanctions%2C%20which%20makes%20Saudi%20interest%20in%20the%20Rafale%20seem%20%26quot%3Brealistic%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20said.%20%26quot%3BSaudi%20Arabia%20wants%20to%20diversify%20its%20air%20force%20so%20that%20if%20it%20has%20an%20interruption%20with%20one%20of%20its%20arm%20suppliers%2C%20like%20the%20United%20States%2C%20its%20air%20wing%20doesn't%20grind%20to%20a%20halt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EShifting%20US-Saudi%20ties%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221683%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biden%20and%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20(MBS)%20fist%20bumping.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62d1976ab0ab4f001853eb81%3F