E%2C%20the%20OpenAI%20CEO%20and%20former%20Y%20Combinator%20head%20with%20whom%20she%20had%20connected%20with%20during%20her%20time%20there.%20She%20had%20followed%20his%20work%20with%20large%20language%20models%20like%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3EGPT-4%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20asked%20him%20if%20this%20was%20the%20missing%20piece%20that%20could%20make%20Milo%20work.%20He%20quickly%20responded%20and%20told%20her%20she%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20and%20put%20her%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20connection%20led%20her%20to%20a%20new%20hire%2C%20her%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20Archa%20Jain%2C%20who%20went%20through%20Y%20Combinator%20with%20her%20startup%20Insight%20Browser%20in%202019.%20It%20also%20led%20to%20a%20fresh%20infusion%20of%20cash%20from%20OpenAI%20to%20keep%20building%20Milo.%20She%20then%20had%20access%20to%20OpenAI's%20models%20as%20the%20foundation%20to%20build%20Milo%20on%20top%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20AI%20assistants%20are%20associated%20with%20how%20they%20can%20enhance%20people's%20work%2C%20but%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20they%20saw%20the%20potential%20beyond%20that%20realm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20never%20hear%20someone%20talk%20about%20the%20power%20of%20these%20models%20to%20help%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brad%20Lightcap%2C%20OpenAI's%20chief%20operating%20officer.%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20OpenAI's%20models%20could%20be%20powering%20that%20experience%20is%20what%20really%20sold%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Milo%2C%20parents%20can%20send%20text%20messages%20of%20grocery%20lists%2C%20photos%20of%20permission%20slips%20or%20sign-up-sheets%20for%20school%20activities%20to%20the%20Milo%20chatbot.%20Milo%20then%20scans%20the%20documents%20and%20predicts%20the%20next%20command%20for%20an%20action%20item%2C%20whether%20it's%20to%20add%20a%20remind