0probably%20discovered%20what%20many%20have%3A%20it%20can%20be%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20backyard%20homes%2C%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadu-tiny-home-pros-cons-construction-housing-costs-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccessory%20dwelling%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20ADUs%2C%20are%20small%20housing%20units%20that%20homeowners%20can%20build%20on%20their%20property.%20They%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hcd.ca.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2022-07%2FADUHandbookUpdate.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20can%20range%20from%3C%2Fa%3E%20150%20square%20feet%20to%20about%201%2C200%20square%20feet%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20the%20unit%20itself%20can%20run%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.renofi.com%2Flearn%2Fadu%2Fcost%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earound%20%24100%2C000%20to%20%24300%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThen%20there's%20also%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20permit.%20In%20California%2C%20where%20most%20backyard%20homes%20are%20being%20built%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backyardunlimited.com%2Faccessory-dwelling-units%2Fresources%2Fadu-costs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPermitting%2520Your%2520ADU%26amp%3Btext%3DDepending%2520on%2520your%2520location%252C%2520you%2Crun%2520from%2520%2524450%2520to%2520%252415%252C000.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EADU%20building%20permits%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%20anywhere%20from%20%24450%20to%20%2415%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20even%20before%20construction%20starts%2C%20according%20to%20Backyard%20Unlimited%2C%20a%20company%20that%20builds%20ADUs.%20There%20could%20be%20other%20costs%20too%2C%20like%20site%20preparation%2C%20which%20includes%20anything%20from%20