Cp%3EAmid%20recent%20tensions%20between%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20Congress%20over%20comments%20on%20Delhi%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20clarified%20that%20he%20will%20attend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flogo-of-india-bloc-likely-to-be-unveiled-during-mumbai-meet-on-september-1-4314120%5C%22%3Ethe%20Opposition%20alliance's%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Alka%20Lamba%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20miffed%20AAP%20with%20her%20%26quot%3Bpreparing%20on%20all%20seven%20Delhi%20seats%26quot%3B%20remark%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20party's%20top%20leadership%20to%20review%20its%20preparedness%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20on%20whether%20to%20have%20an%20alliance%2C%20but%20we%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20prepare%20ourselves%20on%20all%20seven%20seats.%20We%20will%20go%20to%20the%20people%20strongly%20after%20preparing%20ourselves%20properly%20in%20all%20seven%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20hit%20back%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20point%20of%20attending%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20if%20the%20Congress%20wants%20to%20go%20solo%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20go%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20will%20let%20you%20know%20about%20our%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20told%20reporters%20after%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20party%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20AAP%20of%20%26quot%3Bacting%20jumpy%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Falliance-or-not-congress-leader-tweaks-7-seats-comment-as-aap-fumes-4308812%5C%22%3Eon%20Friday%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Alka%20Lamba's%20remark%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20might%20be%20two%20reasons%20for%20AAP%20getting%20jumpy%20in%20this%20case.%20One%20is%20that%20they%20might%20have%20got%20an%20indication%20from%20Amit%20Shah's%20speech%20where%20he%20said%20'AAP%20will%20quit%20INDIA'%20and%20they%20often%20listen%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Secondly%2C%20AAP%20might%20be%20missing%20out%20on%20being%20a%20party%20that%20is%20talked%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20there%20is%20no%20controversy%20over%20the%20alliance%20and%20that%20the%20AAP's%20statement%20is%20either%20a%20%26quot%3Btactic%20to%20blackmail%20them%20or%20stay%20in%20the%20news.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20543%20seats%20and%20no%20other%20parties%20are%20talking%20like%20this%20about%20alliance.%20Samajwadi%20party%20in%20UP%20is%20going%20to%20have%20far%20bigger%20bearing.%20There%20is%20no%20controversy%20on%20alliance.%20It%20is%20the%20AAP%20that%20has%20to%20tell%20us%20if%20they%20are%20preparing%20the%20ground%20to%20move%20away%20or%20not.%20AAP's%20statement%20is%20either%20a%20tactic%20to%20blackmail%20or%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20news%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20are%20way%20different%20from%20the%20AAP%20politically%2C%20but%20if%20they%20modify%20themselves%20and%20comply%20with%20the%20Congress%20central%20leadership%2C%20we%20will%20support%20them.%20The%20decision%20for%20an%20alliance%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20logo%20of%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20unveiled%20during%20the%20front's%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031%20and%20September%201%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApproximately%2080%20leaders%20from%20more%20than%2026%20political%20parties%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20meeting%20in%20the%20country's%20financial%20capital.%20At%20present%2C%2026%20parties%20are%20part%20of%20the%20grouping%20and%20a%20few%20more%20are%20set%20to%20join%20the%20alliance%20during%20the%20two-day%20meeting%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%2C%20known%20by%20its%20abbreviation%20INDIA%2C%20is%20an%20opposition%20front%20announced%20by%20the%20leaders%20of%2026%20parties%20to%20contest%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20to%20challenge%20the%20incumbent%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20opposition%20bloc's%20first%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Patna%20in%20June%20and%20the%20second%20in%20Bengaluru%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692610320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fr4cgkh0g_arvind-kejriwal-satna-madhya-pradesh_625x300_20_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faam-aadmi-party-to-attend-india-alliances-mumbai-meeting-4315520%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20clarified%20that%20he%20will%20attend%20the%20Opposition%20alliance's%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faam-aadmi-party-to-attend-india-alliances-mumbai-meeting-4315520%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faam-aadmi-party-to-attend-india-alliances-mumbai-meeting-4315520%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faam-aadmi-party-to-attend-india-alliances-mumbai-meeting-4315520%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dwarka%20Expressway%3A%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%20About%20India's%20First%208-Lane%20Highway%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUnion%20Transport%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20on%20Sunday%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20glimpses%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-nitin-gadkari-introduces-marvel-of-engineering-dwarka-expressway-4314405%5C%22%3EDwarka%20Expressway%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Northern%20Peripheral%20Road%20or%20NH%20248-BB.%20The%2027.6%20km%20long%20project%20is%20currently%20under%20construction%20and%20will%20connect%20Delhi's%20Dwarka%20with%20Kherki%20Daula%20toll%20plaza%20in%20Gurugram.%20Calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmarvel%20of%20engineering%E2%80%9D%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%20that%20the%20project%20will%20be%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20in%20three%20to%20four%20months.%20The%20transport%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20people%20travelling%20on%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20will%20remember%20the%20experience%20for%20100%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%20in%20five%20points%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20expressway%20will%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Dwarka%20to%20Manesar%20to%2015%20minutes.%20The%20distance%20between%20Manesar%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20can%20now%20be%20covered%20in%2020%20minutes%20while%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Manesar%20and%20Singhu%20border%20will%20come%20down%20to%20just%2045%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Dwarka%20expressway%20has%20been%20built%20using%20two%20lakh%20tonnes%20of%20steel%20--%2030%20times%20what%20took%20to%20build%20the%20Eiffel%20Tower%20in%20Paris.%20Besides%20steel%2C%20about%2020%20lakh%20cubic%20meters%20of%20cement%20concrete%2C%20six%20times%20what%20was%20used%20to%20build%20Dubai's%20Burj%20Khalifa%2C%20went%20into%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMarvel%20of%20Engineering%3A%20The%20Dwarka%20Expressway!%20A%20State-of-the-Art%20Journey%20into%20the%20Future%20%3F%3F%3F%3F%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDwarkaExpressway%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DwarkaExpressway%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPragatiKaHighway%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PragatiKaHighway%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FGatiShakti%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23GatiShakti%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQhgd77WatW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQhgd77WatW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20(%40nitin_gadkari)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnitin_gadkari%2Fstatus%2F1693282411109646561%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2020%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20expressway%20starts%20at%20the%2020-km%20mark%20of%20NH%2048%20(old%20NH%208)%20at%20Shiv%20Murti%20in%20Mahipalpur%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20ends%20at%20the%2040-km%20mark%20near%20Kherki%20Daula%20Toll%20Plaza%20in%20Gurugram.%20It's%20been%20planned%20as%20an%20alternate%20road%20link%20between%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20Gurugram%20to%20ease%20the%20traffic%20on%20the%20Delhi-Gurugram%20Expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnce%20functional%2C%20this%20will%20be%20India's%20first%20eight-lane%20elevated%20expressway.%20The%20total%20length%20of%20the%20four-pack%20motorway%20is%20563%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20During%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%2C%20at%20least%201%2C200%20trees%20were%20re-transplanted%2C%20another%20first%20for%20India.%20Besides%20that%2C%20the%20country's%20first%208-lane%203.6%20km%20long%20urban%20tunnel%20also%20forms%20part%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692610320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fkc48qvk_dwarka-expressway_625x300_20_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-all-you-need-to-know-about-indias-first-8-lane-highway-4315349%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Transport%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20on%20Sunday%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20glimpses%20of%20the%20Dwarka%20Expressway%2C%20also%20called%20the%20Northern%20Peripheral%20Road%20or%20NH%20248-BB.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-all-you-need-to-know-about-indias-first-8-lane-highway-4315349%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-all-you-need-to-know-about-indias-first-8-lane-highway-4315349%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdwarka-expressway-all-you-need-to-know-about-indias-first-8-lane-highway-4315349%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%20Raped%20By%20Delhi%20Officer%20Was%20Hospitalised%20After%20Panic%20Attacks%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%20who%20was%20allegedly%20raped%20by%20a%20senior%20Delhi%20government%20officer%20revealed%20the%20abuse%20to%20doctors%20after%20being%20hospitalised%20for%20a%20string%20of%20panic%20attacks%2C%20police%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPremoday%20Khakha%20is%20accused%20of%20raping%20the%20teen%2C%20his%20friend's%20daughter%2C%20repeatedly%20over%20a%20five-month%20period%20from%20October%202020%20to%20February%202021.%20The%20teenager%2C%20then%2014%2C%20became%20pregnant%20during%20this%20period.%20Khakha's%20wife%20allegedly%20gave%20her%20abortion%20pills%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy%20at%20home%20while%20keeping%20the%20matter%20under%20wraps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20mental%20toll%20of%20what%20she%20went%20through%20that%20the%20teenager%20suffered%20a%20string%20of%20panic%20attacks.%20Alarmed%2C%20her%20mother%20rushed%20her%20to%20a%20hospital.%20The%20girl%20was%20provided%20psychological%20therapy%2C%20during%20which%20she%20told%20doctors%20about%20the%20repeated%20sexual%20assault%20she%20faced%20from%20her%20father's%20friend%2C%20someone%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Bmama%26quot%3B%20(uncle).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20alerted%20police%2C%20who%20moved%20fast%20to%20register%20a%20child%20abuse%20case%20and%20start%20action.%20%26quot%3BWe%20registered%20a%20case%20on%20August%2013%2C%20a%20week%20after%20the%20girl%20was%20hospitalised%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20senior%20police%20officer%20Sagar%20Singh%20Kalsi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20Khakha%20was%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20girl's%20father%2C%20who%20died%20in%202020.%20Following%20his%20death%2C%20the%20girl's%20mother%20sent%20her%20to%20Khakha's%20Burari%20home%20to%20stay%20with%20him%20and%20his%20wife.%20During%20her%20five%20months%20there%2C%20she%20faced%20repeated%20sexual%20assault%2C%20the%20FIR%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20the%20girl%20is%20not%20in%20a%20condition%20yet%20to%20give%20a%20statement%20before%20a%20magistrate.%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20are%20making%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20is%20done%20as%20soon%20as%20she%20feels%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20against%20the%20officer%20have%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-orders-suspension-of-delhi-officer-charged-with-rape-4314956%5C%22%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20moving%20to%20suspend%20him.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20has%20said%20the%20officer%20had%20committed%20a%20%26quot%3Bheinous%20act%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20%26quot%3Bshaken%20the%20society%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20has%20daughters%2C%20and%20this%20is%20a%20very%20shameful%20act.%20The%20officer%20should%20be%20punished%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20of%20the%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairperson%20of%20Delhi%20Commission%20for%20Women%20Swati%20Maliwal%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20demanding%20Khakha's%20immediate%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20one%20whose%20job%20is%20to%20protect%20the%20daughters%20turns%20into%20a%20predator%2C%20then%20where%20will%20the%20girls%20go%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692610320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fm7qan2cg_delhi-officer-premoday-khakha_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-women-and-child-development-department-premoday-khakha-delhi-officer-teen-raped-by-delhi-officer-was-hospitalised-after-string-of-panic-attacks-4315423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Damning%20allegations%20of%20child%20abuse%20against%20senior%20Delhi%20government%20officer%20Premoday%20Khakha%20came%20to%20light%20after%20the%20teen%20survivor%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised%20due%20to%20panic%20attacks%2C%20police%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-women-and-child-development-department-premoday-khakha-delhi-officer-teen-raped-by-delhi-officer-was-hospitalised-after-string-of-panic-attacks-4315423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-women-and-child-development-department-premoday-khakha-delhi-officer-teen-raped-by-delhi-officer-was-hospitalised-after-string-of-panic-attacks-4315423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-women-and-child-development-department-premoday-khakha-delhi-officer-teen-raped-by-delhi-officer-was-hospitalised-after-string-of-panic-attacks-4315423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99ve%20had%20this%20black%20cloud%20looming%20over%20me%E2%80%99%3A%20How%20private%20lenders%20have%20left%20millions%20of%20college%20students%20with%20no%20hope%20for%20the%20future%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20piggy%20bank%20is%20surrounded%20by%20a%20hurricane%20of%20student%20loan%20papers%2C%20unable%20to%20escape.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dd48cc4ef9f30019f8a8fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221101%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20the%20political%20fight%20over%20student-loan%20forgiveness%2C%20people%20with%20private%20student%20debt%20are%20stuck%20with%20predatory%20loan%20terms%20they%20can't%20escape.%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Brianne%20Jones%20graduated%20from%20Eastern%20Michigan%20University%20in%202013%2C%20she%20was%20overjoyed%20to%20have%20a%20college%20degree%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20her%20daunting%20%2442%2C000%20debt%20load.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20figured%20if%20she%20worked%20hard%20and%20kept%20up%20with%20her%20payments%2C%20she%20would%20eventually%20be%20free%20of%20the%20financial%20burden.%20But%20after%2010%20years%20of%20consistent%20payments%2C%20she's%20still%20stuck%20with%20her%20debt%2C%20and%20it%20has%20actually%20grown%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%20%2457%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20twin%20brother%20were%20first-generation%20college%20students%2C%20so%20the%20complexities%20of%20financial%20aid%20were%20foreign%20to%20their%20family.%20When%20they%20maxed%20out%20on%20the%20federal%20aid%20the%20government%20would%20give%20them%2C%20they%20turned%20to%20the%20private%20student-loan%20industry%20to%20complete%20their%20degrees.%20And%20that's%20when%20the%20real%20trouble%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20graduated%20with%20an%20initial%20%2411%2C000%20balance%20in%20private%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20which%20seemed%20manageable%20compared%20with%20her%20federal%20debt%20load%20of%20%2431%2C000.%20But%20while%20she's%20seen%20the%20federal%20balance%20decline%20slightly%2C%20her%20private%20balance%20has%20ballooned%20to%20%2427%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20%24500%20a%20month%20she%20pays%20toward%20the%20loan.%20The%20issue%2C%20Jones%20told%20me%2C%20is%20the%2017.5%25%20interest%20rate%20on%20the%20loans%2C%20which%20is%20nearly%20three%20times%20the%20rate%20on%20her%20federal%20loan.%20This%20astronomically%20high%20rate%20has%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20her%20to%20make%20headway%20on%20the%20private%20part%20of%20her%20debt%3A%20She%20has%20accrued%20%2442%2C000%20in%20interest%20since%20she%20graduated.%20Jones%20has%20gotten%20some%20relief%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%20with%20the%20federal%20student-loan%20payment%20pause%2C%20but%20she's%20worried%20that%20she'll%20fall%20even%20further%20behind%20on%20her%20private%20loans%20when%20those%20payments%20restart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20struggling%20right%20now%2C%20especially%20with%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20her%20and%20her%20brother.%20%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20a%20gallon%20of%20milk%20is%20astronomical%20right%20now.%20Both%20of%20us%20work%20different%20jobs%20to%20make%20money%20on%20the%20side.%20We%20both%20do%20DoorDash%2C%20and%20probably%20when%20those%20federal%20student%20loans%20start%20up%2C%20it'll%20be%20more%20of%20a%20necessity%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20private%20debt%20makes%20up%20just%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20%241.7%20trillion%20student-debt%20mountain%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20about%20%24136%20billion%20%E2%80%94%20the%20industry%20has%20exploded%20over%20the%20past%20decade%3A%20the%20amount%20of%20outstanding%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fticas.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2Fclassof2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20debt%20has%20jumped%20an%20estimated%2047%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202014.%20And%20while%20data%20on%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20borrowers%20is%20difficult%20to%20come%20by%2C%20experts%20estimate%20as%20many%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotectborrowers.org%2Fthe-cares-act-leaves-behind-millions-of-student-loan-borrowers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E6.4%20million%20Americans%20could%20hold%20private%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20political%20furor%20over%20student-loan%20forgiveness%2C%20private-loan%20holders%20are%20not%20only%20left%20out%20of%20the%20federal-relief%20conversation%20but%20also%20forced%20to%20navigate%20a%20hard-to-regulate%20industry%20that%20sometimes%20leaves%20borrowers%20with%20predatory%20loan%20terms%20they%20can't%20escape.%20For%20Jones%2C%20the%20crushing%20weight%20of%20her%20loan%20has%20forced%20her%20to%20pick%20up%20side%20jobs%20and%20try%20to%20pay%20it%20off%20as%20fast%20as%20she%20can%20%E2%80%94%20a%20desperate%20race%20against%20the%20ever-soaring%20interest%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20we're%20trying%20to%20just%20have%20a%20debt%20wiped%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20paying%20what%20we%20owe%2C%20but%20we're%20not%20fine%20with%20paying%20five%20times%20what%20we%20borrowed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20Wild%20West%20for%20students'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20student%20loans%20have%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20since%20the%20Federal%20Direct%20Loan%20Program%20began%20in%201992%2C%20many%20student-loan%20borrowers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20obtain%20funds%20directly%20from%20the%20government.%20The%20federal%20loan%20program%20offered%20lower%20interest%20rates%20and%20standardized%20terms%2C%20which%20was%20immediately%20appealing%20to%20borrowers.%20But%20surging%20tuition%20costs%20and%20the%20shrinking%20amount%20of%20nonloan%20financial%20aid%20available%20to%20students%20have%20helped%20fuel%20the%20recent%20demand%20for%20private%20loans.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20Institute%20for%20College%20Access%20%26amp%3B%20Success'%20senior%20director%20of%20college%20affordability%2C%20Michele%20Shepard%2C%20told%20me%2C%20students%20take%20on%20private%20debt%20when%20they've%20tapped%20out%20the%20maximum%20amount%20of%20federal%20loans%20they%20can%20hold%20%E2%80%94%20%245%2C500%20for%20a%20first-year%20student%20who%20is%20a%20tax%20dependent%20or%20%249%2C500%20for%20independent%20students.%20Though%20that%20number%20rises%20for%20each%20year%20of%20education%2C%20it's%20often%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20just%20don't%20have%20the%20money%20out%20of%20pocket%20to%20cover%20their%20costs%20even%20after%20they've%20taken%20out%20all%20their%20federal%20loans%2C%26quot%3B%20Shepard%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20that's%20often%20where%20you%20see%20someone%20will%20say%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20get%20that%20extra%20money%2C'%20and%20they%20will%20turn%20to%20the%20private%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20students%20turn%20to%20the%20private%20market%2C%20they%20find%20a%20litany%20of%20lenders%20willing%20to%20help%20fund%20their%20education%20dreams.%20But%20despite%20lofty%20promises%20from%20private%20lenders%2C%20Shepard%20told%20me%20it's%20all%20about%20making%20a%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20so%20expensive%20that%20they%20are%20destined%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ESuzanne%20Martindale%2C%20the%20senior%20deputy%20commissioner%20for%20consumer%20protection%20at%20California's%20Department%20of%20Financial%20Protection%20and%20Innovation%2C%20told%20me%20that%20the%20issue%20with%20borrowers%20seeking%20out%20private%20lenders%20was%20%26quot%3Bthat%20there%20has%20not%20been%20a%20ton%20of%20federal%20oversight.%20She%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there%20really%20isn't%20much%20by%20way%20of%20federal%20regulation%20to%20govern%20those%20kinds%20of%20products%20and%20services.%26quot%3B%20The%20ability%20for%20private%20lenders%20to%20have%20the%20freedom%20largely%20to%20set%20their%20own%20terms%2C%20Shepard%20said%2C%20has%20turned%20the%20market%20into%20%26quot%3Ba%20Wild%20West%20for%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20variability%20with%20interest%20rates%20plays%20a%20large%20role%20in%20the%20%26quot%3BWild%20West%26quot%3B%20setting.%20While%20rates%20on%20federal%20loans%20are%20fixed%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20the%20rate%20that%20is%20set%20when%20a%20borrower%20takes%20out%20the%20loan%20will%20stay%20the%20same%20for%20the%20lifetime%20of%20the%20loan%20%E2%80%94%20some%20private%20student%20loans%20are%20variable%2C%20meaning%20the%20rate%20can%20increase%20or%20decrease%20as%20a%20borrower%20pays%20it%20off%20and%20lenders%20can%20set%20their%20own%20rates.%20With%20situations%20like%20Jones'%2C%20when%20the%20rate%20is%20in%20the%20double%20digits%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20the%20mounting%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20loans%20are%20so%20expensive%20that%20they%20are%20destined%20to%20fail.%20In%20other%20cases%2C%20borrowers%20ran%20into%20unexpected%20life%20traumas%20such%20as%20disabilities%20or%20divorces%20that%20ruin%20their%20dreams%20of%20upward%20mobility%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20National%20Consumer%20Law%20Center%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.studentloanborrowerassistance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F05%2FReport_PrivateLoans.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%202008%20paper.%20%26quot%3BRegardless%2C%20the%20student%20loan%20debt%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20an%20investment%20in%20their%20futures%20is%20dragging%20them%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20predatory%20lending%20trap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20between%20study%20sessions%2C%20exams%2C%20and%20campus%20parties%2C%20deciphering%20complex%20student-loan%20terms%20has%20become%20a%20standard%20part%20of%20students'%20higher-education%20experience.%20To%20improve%20their%20life%20prospects%2C%2018-%20and%2019-year-olds%20are%20expected%20to%20comb%20through%20pages%20of%20virtual%20paperwork%20and%20go%20%26quot%3Binterest-rate%20shopping%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20which%20lender%20has%20the%20best%20terms.%20And%20complex%20terms%20can%20end%20up%20getting%20these%20students%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20families%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20financial%20bind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20more%20common%20and%20innocuous-sounding%20actions%20a%20borrower%20might%20take%20is%20bringing%20on%20a%20cosigner%2C%20Anna%20Anderson%2C%20a%20staff%20attorney%20with%20the%20National%20Consumer%20Law%20Center%20focusing%20primarily%20on%20student-loan%20issues%2C%20told%20me.%20While%20cosigners%20are%20necessary%20to%20help%20out%20borrowers%20who%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20loan%20on%20their%20own%2C%20the%20agreement%20can%20end%20up%20leaving%20the%20cosigner%20in%20a%20hole%20that's%20tricky%20to%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20who%20is%20just%20looking%20to%20help%20their%20loved%20one%20get%20the%20education%20that%20they%20think%20they%20deserve%2C%20those%20folks%2C%20when%20they%20sign%20up%20for%20these%20loans%2C%20they%20don't%20always%20understand%20the%20financial%20consequences%20and%20risks%20that%20come%20with%20these%20and%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20you%20remove%20yourself%20from%20that%20loan%20once%20you've%20agreed%20to%20be%20a%20cosigner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EIt's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20low-income%20and%20more%20vulnerable%20populations%20that%20often%20get%20really%20aggressively%20targeted%20for%20these%20programs%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20once%20borrowers%20sign%20on%20the%20dotted%20line%2C%20they%20open%20themselves%20up%20to%20aggressive%20debt%20collection%20and%20misleading%20behavior%2C%20such%20as%20communications%20from%20the%20lenders%20that%20do%20not%20clearly%20disclose%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20loan.%20These%20tactics%20have%20started%20attracting%20the%20attention%20of%20federal%20and%20state%20regulators.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20January%202022%2C%2039%20state%20attorneys%20general%20announced%20they%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavient-student-loan-settlement-attorneys-general-debt-relief-borrowers-2022-1%5C%22%3Ereached%20a%20%241.85%20billion%20settlement%20with%20Navient%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20servicer%20of%20private%20loans%20%E2%80%94%20over%20allegations%20of%20%26quot%3Bwidespread%20unfair%2C%20deceptive%2C%20and%20abusive%20student%20loan%20servicing%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said.%20They%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20offering%20private%20student%20loans%20to%20borrowers%20who%20went%20to%20for-profit%20schools%20regardless%20of%20their%20abilities%20to%20pay%20the%20loans%20back.%20Navient%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20from%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%20told%20me%20that%20private-loan%20originators%2C%20servicers%2C%20and%20collectors%20remained%20subject%20to%20a%20number%20of%20federal%20laws%2C%20including%20the%20Truth%20in%20Lending%20Act%2C%20that%20were%20designed%20to%20protect%20consumers%20from%20predatory%20behavior.%20And%20Martindale%20said%20the%20people%20targeted%20by%20predatory%20behavior%20were%20often%20%26quot%3Bfolks%20who%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20resources%2C%20maybe%20working%20a%20low-wage%20job%20and%20trying%20to%20better%20themselves%20and%20their%20future.%26quot%3B%20Martindale%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20the%20low-income%20and%20more%20vulnerable%20populations%20that%20often%20get%20really%20aggressively%20targeted%20for%20these%20programs.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20federal%20benefits%20for%20private%20borrowers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20subjected%20to%20the%20sales%20tactics%20and%20pernicious%20whims%20of%20their%20private%20lender%2C%20once%20a%20borrower%20enters%20business%20with%20a%20private%20lender%2C%20they%20immediately%20lose%20the%20hope%20of%20getting%20any%20relief%20from%20the%20federal%20government.%20Ryan%20Moran%2C%20a%20nurse%20at%20an%20intensive-care%20unit%20in%20Florida%2C%20has%20about%20%2475%2C000%20in%20private%20student%20debt%2C%20along%20with%20a%20%2438%2C000%20federal%20balance.%20He%20wanted%20to%20further%20his%20education%20by%20going%20to%20grad%20school%20and%20hopefully%20boost%20his%20salary%2C%20but%20his%20private%20lender%20would%20not%20defer%20payments%20while%20he%20was%20in%20school%20%E2%80%94%20as%20federal%20loans%20allow%20a%20student%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20making%20the%20option%20unaffordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20put%20my%20life%20on%20pause%20for%20multiple%20years%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Moran%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20kind%20of%20the%20push%20and%20pull%20between%20making%20the%20minimum%20payment%20for%2020%2C%2025%20years%20and%20paying%20all%20that%20interest%20or%20just%20working%20overtime%20every%20week%20for%20five%20years%20to%20pay%20everything%20off%20and%20putting%20my%20entire%20life%20on%20hold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoran%20isn't%20alone.%20While%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20pushed%20through%20targeted%20relief%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-administration-will-forgive-39-billion-in-student-debt-2023-7%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20federal%20borrowers%20in%20the%20past%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20does%20not%20have%20the%20jurisdiction%20to%20offer%20relief%20programs%20to%20people%20with%20private%20lenders.%20That%20means%20private%20borrowers%20didn't%20benefit%20from%20the%20student-loan-payment%20pause%20that%20began%20in%20March%202020%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20wouldn't%20have%20been%20included%20in%20Biden's%20plan%20to%20cancel%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20student%20debt%20per%20borrower%20had%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20that%20federal%20student-loan%20payments%20are%20resuming%20in%20October%20after%20an%20almost%20four-year%20pause%2C%20it's%20even%20more%20pressing%20that%20borrowers%20know%20exactly%20what%20they%20could%20miss%20out%20on%20by%20shifting%20to%20private%20loans.%20Many%20lenders%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20this%20moment%20to%20offer%20people%20with%20federal%20loans%20refinancing%20services%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allows%20a%20borrower%20to%20move%20their%20loans%20to%20a%20new%20lender%20under%20different%20terms.%20Refinancing%20companies%20typically%20emphasize%20the%20monthly%20savings%20a%20borrower%20could%20receive%20by%20shifting%20to%20a%20new%2C%20lower-interest%20rate.%20But%20if%20a%20borrower%20with%20federal%20student%20loans%20refinances%20to%20a%20private%20lender%2C%20it%20will%20strip%20them%20of%20all%20of%20their%20federal%20benefits%2C%20including%20forgiveness%20and%20repayment%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3ESince%20I%20started%20college%2C%20I've%20just%20had%20this%20black%20cloud%20looming%20over%20me%20knowing%20I%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20off%20this%20debt%20eventually.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EShepard%20said%20refinancing%20could%20bring%20some%20benefits%20to%20borrowers%2C%20but%20for%20others%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frefinance-student-debt-trap-biden-loan-forgiveness-supreme-court-2023-2%5C%22%3Erefinancing%20can%20be%20a%20trap%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20concerns%20me%20is%20that%20most%20people%20are%20put%20in%20a%20position%20where%20they%20don't%20really%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20choices%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20Anderson%20of%20the%20National%20Consumer%20Law%20Center%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Breally%20concerned%20about%20refinancing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20private%20servicers%20do%20disclose%20benefits%20private%20borrowers%20could%20lose%20should%20they%20choose%20to%20refinance.%20Navient%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20a%20disclosure%20on%20its%20website%20that%20says%20refinancing%20a%20federal%20student%20loan%20%26quot%3Bmeans%20you%20will%20no%20longer%20have%20access%20to%20federal%20loan%20benefits%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bany%20other%20relief%20measures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoFi%2C%20another%20refinancing%20company%2C%20sent%20letters%20in%20the%20mail%20to%20borrowers%20with%20the%20header%3A%20%26quot%3BFederal%20student%20loan%20forbearance%20is%20ending%20soon.%20Don't%20miss%20out%20on%20savings%20%E2%80%94%20start%20planning%20your%20refi%20today.%26quot%3B%20Inside%20the%20mailer%2C%20there%20was%20a%20disclosure%20saying%20that%20borrowers%20should%20%26quot%3Bstill%20consider%26quot%3B%20Biden's%20plans%20for%20federal%20debt%20relief%20but%20%26quot%3Bshould%20also%20take%20time%20now%20to%20prepare%20for%20your%20payments%20to%20restart%2C%20including%20the%20opportunity%20to%20refinance%20your%20student%20loan%20debt%20at%20a%20lower%20APR%20or%20to%20extend%20your%20term%20to%20achieve%20a%20lower%20monthly%20payment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHopes%20for%20regulation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20federal%20lenders%20answer%20to%20the%20government%2C%20the%20best%20oversight%20for%20private%20lenders%20at%20the%20moment%20are%20complaints%20submitted%20to%20the%20Consumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%2C%20which%20can%20then%20investigate%20and%20fine%20lending%20firms.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20actions%20are%20confidential%2C%20the%20general%20public%20may%20not%20even%20realize%20a%20lender%20has%20been%20sanctioned.%20And%20despite%20the%20agency%20having%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%2C%20funding%20for%20the%20CFPB%20is%20%26quot%3Bcontinuously%20starved%2C%26quot%3B%20Shepard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20some%20federal%20lawmakers%20have%20been%20working%20to%20expand%20relief%20for%20private%20borrowers.%20In%20January%2C%20Rep.%20Steve%20Cohen%20led%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcohen.house.gov%2Fmedia-center%2Fpress-releases%2Fcongressman-cohen-introduces-private-student-loan-bankruptcy-fairness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereintroduction%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Private%20Student%20Loan%20Bankruptcy%20Fairness%20Act%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20private%20student%20debt%20to%20be%20discharged%20in%20bankruptcy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20standard%20that%20existed%20before%20a%202005%20change%20in%20the%20law.%20Some%20states%20are%20also%20taking%20up%20the%20fight.%20Martindale%20of%20California's%20Department%20of%20Financial%20Protection%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20our%20part%20here%20in%20California%20to%20clarify%20how%20our%20laws%20apply%20to%20these%20kinds%20of%20private%20entities.%26quot%3B%20And%20some%20state%20governments%20have%20established%20a%20%26quot%3Bbill%20of%20rights%26quot%3B%20for%20borrowers%20%E2%80%94%20Maryland%2C%20for%20example%2C%20outlined%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dllr.state.md.us%2Ffinance%2Fconsumers%2Ffrslbillofrights.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elist%20of%20protections%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%202022%20that%20said%20borrowers%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20subjected%20to%20conduct%20that%20is%20intended%20to%20mislead%20you%20or%20otherwise%20treat%20you%20in%20an%20unfair%2C%20abusive%20or%20deceptive%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoran%20said%20he%20didn't%20regret%20taking%20out%20private%20student%20loans%20because%20it%20allowed%20him%20to%20pursue%20his%20desired%20nursing%20career.%20But%20he%20wishes%20turning%20to%20a%20private%20lender%20didn't%20come%20with%20such%20a%20high%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20past%20couple%20of%20years%20have%20been%20paying%20down%20as%20much%20as%20I%20can%20and%20not%20really%20having%20any%20savings%20to%20show%20for%20it%2C%20despite%20having%20a%20decent-paying%20job.%20It's%20kind%20of%20impossible%20to%20get%20ahead%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20prospect%20of%20ownership%20of%20a%20house%20is%20so%20unattainable%20at%20the%20moment%20it's%20almost%20laughable.%20Since%20I%20started%20college%2C%20I've%20just%20had%20this%20black%20cloud%20looming%20over%20me%20knowing%20I%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20off%20this%20debt%20eventually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fayelet-sheffey%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%2233c4ee918afc4fca8c47ebeab08d18cb%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fayelet-sheffey%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%3EAyelet%20Sheffey%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20senior%20economic%20policy%20reporter%20covering%20student%20debt%20on%20Insider's%20economy%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-private-debt-no-relief-interest-rates-payments-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692610081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64dd49054ef9f30019f8a928%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-private-debt-no-relief-interest-rates-payments-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20the%20booming%20market%20for%20private%20loans%20has%20saddled%20millions%20of%20students%20with%20%24136%20billion%20in%20debt%20that%20can't%20be%20forgiven.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22