untry%20cannot%20forget%20the%20days%20before%202014%20when%20there%20were%20rampant%20scams%20and%20corruption.%20Rights%20of%20the%20poor%20were%20looted%20before%202014.%20But%20now%2C%20they%20are%20receiving%20money%20directly%20in%20their%20bank%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20Rozgar%20Mela.%20Citing%20a%20report%20on%20the%20higher%20number%20of%20income%20tax%20returns%20filed%20this%20year%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20are%20coming%20forward%20to%20pay%20taxes%20as%20they%20know%20that%20their%20tax%20is%20being%20used%20for%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Frights-of-poor-looted-in-era-of-scams-corruption-before-2014-pm-modi-at-mp-rozgar-mela%2Farticleshow%2F102898106.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Today%2C%20citizens%20know%20their%20tax%20being%20used%20for%20nation's%20devpt%3A%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692603289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102898161%2Cimgsize-847846.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftoday-citizens-know-their-tax-being-used-for-nations-development-pm-modi-at-mp-rozgar-mela%2Farticleshow%2F102898106.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftoday-citizens-know-their-tax-being-used-for-nations-development-pm-modi-at-mp-rozgar-mela%2Farticleshow%2F102898106.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Is%20Hell%20Bent%20on%20Building%20an%20Administrative%20System%20That%20Treats%20Him%20as%20King%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F11152259%2FIMG_0081.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20increasing%20politicisation%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20has%20been%20corroding%2C%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%20the%20pillars%20on%20which%20fair%20and%20efficient%20administration%20rest.%20The%20pains%20taken%20by%20the%20founding%20fathers%20of%20our%20constitution%20to%20protect%20and%20insulate%20the%20civil%20service%20from%20political%20interference%20had%20ensured%20a%20large%20degree%20of%20neutrality%2C%20for%20several%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20except%20perhaps%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20What%20is%20more%20important%20is%20that%20it%20created%20a%20culture%20of%20looking%20down%20at%20any%20suspiciously%20close%20liaison%20between%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20(for%20mutual%20personal%20gain)%20to%20be%20illicit%20and%20adulterous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recently%20passed%20Delhi%20Services%20Act%20runs%20counter%20to%20this%20ethos%20and%20legitimises%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebabu-neta%3C%2Fem%3E%20nexus.%20While%20asserting%20the%20supremacy%20of%20politics%20and%20administration%20(euphemistically%20called%20the%20executive)%20over%20the%20judiciary%2C%20it%20ensures%20that%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20political%20agenda%20is%20thrust%20on%20an%20elected%20chief%20minister.%20This%20law%20damages%20the%20very%20federal%20structure%2C%20to%20uphold%20which%2C%20the%20all%20India%20services%20were%20created.%20The%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20the%20civil%20service%2C%20enshrined%20in%20List%20II%20of%20the%20Seventh%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20is%20undermined%20by%20legally%20empowering%20the%20chief%20secretary%20and%20the%20home%20secretary%20of%20Delhi%20to%20overrule%20him.%20The%20root%20of%20the%20success%20of%20political%20governance%20that%20lies%20in%20the%20subordinate%20position%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20uprooted%20%E2%80%93%20which%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20exposes%20officers%20to%20a%20field%20that%20is%20full%20of%20pits%20and%20mines.%20It%20is%20not%20that%20senior%20bureaucrats%20have%20never%20differed%20from%20chief%20ministers%2C%20but%20officials%20believe%20that%20when%20two%20persons%20ride%20a%20horse%2C%20one%20has%20to%20ride%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20know%20Narendra%20Modi%20are%2C%20however%2C%20not%20scandalised%20with%20this%20daylight%20politicisation%20of%20the%20administration%2C%20for%20he%20has%20never%20hidden%20his%20contempt%20for%20its%20basic%20principles%20of%20experience%2C%20merit%20and%20seniority.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fixation%20is%20with%20unflinching%20personal%20loyalty%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trait%20that%20both%20the%20law%20and%20centuries%20of%20experience%20discourage.%20An%20open%20structure%20like%20public%20administration%20cannot%20and%20should%20not%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20closed%20private%20limited%20company.%20But%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20basic%20insecurities%20prompt%20him%20to%20pick%20his%20cabal%2C%20often%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20many%20other%20competent%20bureaucrats.%20He%20rewards%C2%A0%20loyalty%20and%20ensures%20that%20every%20officer%20who%20has%20been%20of%20use%20to%20him%20is%20recompensed%2C%20often%20beyond%20his%20dreams.%20This%20strategy%20seeks%20to%20break%20the%20spine%20of%20neutrality%20of%20civil%20servants%20and%20explains%20why%20many%20are%20collaborating%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20grey-to-black-area%20decisions.%20These%20%E2%80%98collaborators%E2%80%99%20are%20banking%20on%20his%20ever-continuing%20rule%2C%20and%20they%20often%20overlook%20the%20fact%20that%20their%20fingerprints%20can%20later%20be%20traced%20in%20the%20controversial%20surrender%20of%20national%20assets%20like%20airports%2C%20port%20areas%2C%20power%20utilities%20and%20coal%20blocks%20to%20cronies.%20These%20will%20reveal%20how%20much%20collaborators%20had%20stretched%20to%20please%20the%20boss.%20It%20is%20good%20to%20remind%20them%20that%20ultimately%20it%20was%20officials%20(even%20upright%20ones)%20who%20were%20given%20jail%20sentences%20in%20the%20coal%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Civil%20Servants%3A%20From%20Colonial%20Clones%20to%20Compliant%20Managers%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-colonial-clones-compliant-managers%5C%22%3ECivil%20Servants%3A%20From%20Colonial%20Clones%20to%20Compliant%20Managers%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20less-discussed%20characteristic%20of%20the%20functioning%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20chief%20minister%20or%20prime%20minister%2C%20is%20his%20sheer%20panic%20with%20the%20English%20language.%20This%20is%20strange%2C%20as%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%20could%20manage%20quite%20well%2C%20with%20a%20judicious%20mix%20of%20languages%20and%20Modi%20has%20the%20credit%20of%20mastering%20a%20second%20language%2C%20Hindi.%20But%20his%20unease%20with%20English%20is%20quite%20visible%20and%20explains%20his%20obsession%20with%20Gujarati%20and%20Hindi.%20He%20is%20not%20embarrassed%20in%20selecting%20a%20grossly%20disproportionate%20number%20of%20officers%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20state%20of%20origin.%20He%20plonks%20them%20in%20most%20critical%20positions%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20omnipotent%20principal%20secretary%20in%20the%20PMO%20to%20heads%20of%20several%20agencies%20through%20which%20he%20spreads%20terror.%20They%20explain%20files%20and%20reports%20to%20him%20in%20Gujarati%20or%20in%20Hindi%2C%20and%20he%20confesses%20that%20he%20is%20loathe%20to%20read%20the%20written%20word.%20Working%20in%20Gujarat%20becomes%20an%20unimaginable%20asset%2C%20and%20even%20a%20private%20sector%20employee%20of%20a%20crony%20company%20now%20wields%20the%20whip%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20limitations%20restrict%20his%20choice%20severely%20and%20explains%20the%20third%2C%20i.e.%20why%20he%20hates%20to%20let%20go%20of%20these%20henchmen.%20His%20distrust%20of%20non-tested%20officers%20is%20just%20too%20strongly%20embedded%20in%20his%20psyche%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20present%20cabinet%20secretary%20and%20home%20secretary%20are%20on%20perpetual%20extension.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20first%20law%20he%20amended%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20became%20prime%20minister%20was%20to%20get%20over%20a%20legal%20prohibition%20and%20have%20a%20bland%20but%20trusted%20retired%20officer%20as%20his%20principal%20secretary.%20The%20extension%20after%20extension%20that%20Sanjay%20Mishra%20continues%20to%20get%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20now-notorious%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20vindicates%20his%20clutching-on%20habit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Modi%2C%20Faustian%20babu-neta%20bargains%20are%20reportedly%20on%20the%20rise%2C%20even%20if%20they%20wreck%20civil%20service%20ethics%20and%20ethos.%20The%20civil%20service%20continues%2C%20however%2C%20to%20remain%20attractive%20despite%20severe%20criticism%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20which%20is%20misplaced.%20Every%20year%2C%20several%20lakh%20youth%20still%20compete%20for%20the%20less%20than%20a%20thousand%20top%20posts%20in%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20the%20civil%20service.%20This%20fresh%20blood%20transfusion%20helps%20maintain%20the%20best%20stream%20possible%2C%20and%20it%20is%20commendable%20that%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20bureaucracy%20does%20not%20connive%20to%20benefit%20the%20regime%E2%80%99s%20favoured%20plutocrats%20and%20oligarchs.%20This%20is%20evident%20from%20the%20reluctance%20of%20the%20conscientious%20officers%20to%20allow%20wholesale%20privatisation%20of%20national%20assets%20at%20throwaway%20value%20or%20even%20to%20indulge%20in%20questionable%20lease%20of%20government%20properties.%20This%20invited%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20bitter%20wrath%20at%20the%20IAS%2C%20some%20time%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20'The%20IAS%20Has%20Failed%20India%20and%20Must%20Change'%3A%20Ex-RBI%20Governor%20Duvvuri%20Subbarao%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwatch-the-ias-has-failed-india-and-must-change-ex-rbi-governor-duvvuri-subbarao%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20IAS%20Has%20Failed%20India%20and%20Must%20Change%E2%80%99%3A%20Ex-RBI%20Governor%20Duvvuri%20Subbarao%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerror%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20favoured%20instrument%20and%20affects%20many%20an%20officer.%20He%20is%20not%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20only%20one%20who%20uses%20this%20patronage-or-punishment%20choice%2C%20but%20he%20has%20sunk%20it%20to%20dizzying%20depths.%20How%20else%20how%20does%20one%20explain%20the%20stock-market%20regulator%20SEBI%20looking%20the%20other%20way%20when%20the%20valuation%20of%20questionable%20companies%20went%20up%20by%205%2C000%25%20in%20three%20years%3F%20Finance%20ministry%20officials%20of%20that%20period%20cannot%20claim%20to%20be%20unaware%20of%20what%20was%20happening.%20Similarly%2C%20those%20in%20the%20coal%20and%20power%20ministries%20can%20hardly%20feign%20innocence%20while%20framing%20policies%20to%20facilitate%20a%20monopolist%20to%20handle%20coal%20import%20at%20costs%20that%20are%208%20to%2010%20times%20higher%20than%20domestic%2C%20and%20extract%20the%20higher%20bills%20from%20us.%20Similarly%2C%20bank%20chiefs%20and%20ministry%20officials%20have%20all%20been%20privy%20to%20(and%20part%20of)%20the%20unprecedented%20write-offs%20done%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20nine%20years%2C%20amounting%20to%20a%20staggering%20Rs%2012.51%20lakh%20crore.%20This%20humungous%20sum%20was%20%E2%80%98adjusted%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccleaning%20account%20books%E2%80%9D%2C%20by%20destroying%20forever%20the%20money%20kept%20in%20banks.%20In%20reality%2C%20however%2C%20cronies%20and%20frauds%20like%20Nirav%20Modi%20and%20Mehul%20Choksi%20could%20get%20away%20and%20splurge%20in%20luxuries%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20regime%20has%20surely%20facilitated%20the%20rich%20to%20become%20incredibly%20richer.%20Ambani%20increased%20his%20wealth%20from%20%2418%20billion%20in%202014%20to%20a%20staggering%20%2490%20billion%20now.%20Adani%2C%20who%20flew%20Modi%20from%20Ahmedabad%20to%20Delhi%20in%20his%20private%20plane%20in%202014%C2%A0%20(sending%20all%20sorts%20of%20signals)%2C%20increased%20his%20worth%20from%20%248%20billion%20then%20to%20an%20unbelievable%20%24140%20billion%20in%20eight%20years.%20Then%2C%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20punctured%20it%20and%20brought%20it%20down%20to%20%2464%20billion%20at%20present%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20still%20sky%20high.%20One%20noticed%20that%20babus%20who%20successfully%20managed%20these%20and%20other%20%E2%80%98best%20friends%E2%80%99%20did%20phenomenally%20well%20in%20service%2C%20and%20even%20in%20politics%20later%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20is%20so%20convoluted%20that%20few%20can%20realise%20how%20this%20regime%20facilitates%20the%20rich%20to%20get%20richer.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20see%20an%20example.%20If%20one%20examines%20India%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20role%20in%20playing%20%E2%80%98neutral%E2%80%99%20during%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20we%20find%20it%20actually%20benefitted%20two%20Indian%20corporates%20of%20Gujarat%20more%20than%20it%20helped%20the%20people%20of%20India.%20While%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20and%20his%20horde%20of%20unusually-biased%20officials%2C%20who%20troll%20anyone%20for%20saying%20the%20truth%2C%20loudly%20justified%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20procure%20cheaper%20Russian%20crude%20by%20defying%20the%20West%20as%20patriotic%2C%20the%20public%20sector%20refineries%20could%20hardly%20gain%20for%20almost%20a%20year.%20They%20were%20bound%20by%20long%20term%20contracts%20to%20source%20their%20supplies%20at%20much%20higher%20prices.%20It%20was%20two%20private%20refineries%20in%20Gujarat%20which%20have%20(with%20low%20obligation%20to%20supply%20oil%20to%20our%20pumps)%20lapped%20up%20cheap%20Russian%20crude%20and%20then%20re-exported%20petro-products%20at%20phenomenal%20profits.%20India%20exported%2098%20million%20tonnes%20of%20petro-products%20for%20%2497%20billion%20in%20the%20Ukraine-shattered%20year%202022-23%20%E2%80%94%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20%2467%20billion%20we%20got%20in%202021-22%2C%20for%20the%20very%20same%20quantity.%20ONGC%20and%20IOC%20are%20prohibited%20by%20the%20government%20to%20export%20and%20make%20profits.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20did%20not%20mention%20that%20the%20Ukraine%20policy%20actually%20enriched%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20cronies.%20Another%20ex-diplomat%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20petroleum%20ministry%20and%20his%20officials%20disclose%20nothing%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20not%20even%20why%20our%20petrol%20prices%20were%20not%20coming%20down%20despite%20lower%20costs%20of%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20profession%20suffers%20a%20few%20pejorative%20terms%20and%20the%20choicest%20one%20for%20bureaucrats%20is%20%E2%80%98courtier%E2%80%99.%20But%20Birbal%20was%20also%20one%20%E2%80%94%20a%20wise%20one.%20Even%20the%20most%20rancid%20critics%20cannot%20deny%20that%20the%20calling%20is%2C%20indeed%2C%20a%20critical%20and%20coveted%20one.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20countless%20wannabes%20hang%20around%20politicians%20till%20late%20at%20night%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20a%20place%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98court%E2%80%99%20of%20political%20governance.%20But%2C%20as%20we%20have%20seen%2C%20most%20constitutionally%20selected%20%E2%80%98courtiers%E2%80%99%20still%20follow%20principles.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20the%20present%20ruler%20does%20not%20appreciate%20this%20and%20rewards%20only%20those%20officials%20or%20courtiers%20who%20dispense%20with%20all%20morality%20to%20please%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawhar-sircar%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fjawha