r%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshoka%20University%20has%20been%20criticised%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20as%20the%20varsity%20had%20publicly%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20after%20the%20political%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20academics%E2%80%99%20full%20statement%20and%20list%20of%20signatories%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%20members%20of%20the%20academic%20fraternity%2C%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20forced%20%E2%80%98resignation%E2%80%99%20of%20Sabyasachi%20Das%2C%20Assistant%20Professor%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Economics%2C%20Ashoka%20University.%20Das%E2%80%99s%20paper%20%E2%80%98Democratic%20Backsliding%20in%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Democracy%E2%80%99%20which%20analysed%20the%20probability%20of%20electoral%20manipulation%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20came%20under%20significant%20flak%20from%20the%20party.%20The%20University%20issued%20a%20statement%20dissociating%20itself%20from%20the%20research.%20Following%20this%2C%20from%20what%20has%20emerged%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20the%20Governing%20Body%20decided%20to%20%E2%80%98evaluate%E2%80%99%20the%20%E2%80%98merit%E2%80%99%20of%20his%20paper.%20Dr%20Das%20subsequently%20resigned.%20It%20is%20clear%20from%20this%20sequence%20of%20events%20that%20what%20was%20at%20stake%20was%20not%20the%20academic%20merit%20of%20his%20paper%2C%20but%20the%20threat%20it%20posed%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20detailed%20academic%20counter%20to%20this%20paper%2C%20only%20ad%20hominem%20attacks%20in%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Pulapre%20Balakrishnan%20of%20the%20Economics%20department%20subsequently%20resigned%20from%20Ashoka%20University%20in%20solidarity%2C%20student%20organisations%20have%20issued%20strong%20statements%20in%20support%20of%20Dr%20Das%2C%20the%20Economics%20department%2C%20followed%20by%20several%20other%20departmen