inal%20laws%20impacting%20freedom%20of%20the%20press%2C%20ceasing%20all%20forms%20of%20%E2%80%98lawfare%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20press%2C%20ensuring%20reported%20cases%20of%20violence%20or%20intimidation%20against%20journalists%20and%20media%20workers%20are%20investigated%20transparently%20and%20independently%2C%20and%20holding%20those%20responsible%20for%20crimes%20against%20journalists%20to%20account%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692597952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F27153145%2FHasina_20170922_402_602.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Finternational-press-institute-bangladesh-digital-security-act%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20media%20watchdog%20has%2C%20however%2C%20called%20for%20consultation%20with%20civil%20society%20to%20ensure%20that%20proposed%20Cyber%20Security%20Act%20is%20compatible%20with%20international%20human%20rights.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Finternational-press-institute-bangladesh-digital-security-act%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deadly%20Storm%20Hilary%20brings%20'life-threatening'%20floods%20and%20record%20rainfall%20to%20California%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692596760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F08%2F768x432%2Fskynews-storm-hilary-california_6257809.jpg%3F20230821082138%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fone-dead-in-mexico-as-storm-hilary-brings-life-threatening-floods-and-record-rainfall-to-california-12944367%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20person%20has%20died%20and%20another%20is%20missing%20as%20a%20tropical%20storm%20brings%20%26quot%3Blife-threatening%26quot%3B%20floods%20and%20record%20rainfall%20to%20Mexico%20and%20California.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A91%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2