ment%20of%20a%20public%20hearing%20for%20the%20project%20in%20early%20August%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(TNPCB).%20The%20TNPCB%20announced%20that%20the%20public%20hearing%20would%20be%20held%20on%20September%205.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20public%20hearing%2C%20project%20proponents%20will%20present%20the%20project%20and%20its%20potential%20impacts%20to%20the%20members%20of%20local%20communities%20and%20stakeholders%20and%20collect%20their%20feedback.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20o%3Cspan%3En%20August%2010%2C%20the%20Tiruvallur%20district%20collector%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpoovulagu%2Fstatus%2F1689567432086892544%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epostponed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20it%2C%20because%20the%20district%20administration%20had%20received%20requests%20that%20public%20hearings%20be%20conducted%20at%20more%20than%20one%20location%20so%20that%20people%20can%20express%20their%20views%20about%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20public%20hearing%20has%20been%20postponed.%20Strong%20opposition%20from%20environmental%20groups%2C%20citizens%20and%20opposition%20parties%20over%20the%20expansion%20of%20Kattupalli%20Port%20had%20prompted%20the%20then-district%20collector%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dtnext.in%2Fcity%2F2021%2F01%2F20%2Fkattupalli-port-development-collector-cancels-public-hearing%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epostpone%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20last%20public%20hearing%20for%20the%20project%20in%20January%202021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fadani-joint-venture-ktv-oil-mills-health-food%5C%22%3EHow%20an%20Adani%20Joint%20Venture%20Tried%20to%20Use%20Semantics%20to%20Circumvent%20Green%20Laws%20%E2%80%93%20at%20Cost%20of%20Fishers