20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20ten%20retired%20civil%20servants%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-within-its-rights-to-shelve-adani-kattupalli-port-plan-former-bureaucrats-write-to-cm%2Farticle36513158.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20Stalin%20and%20the-then%20finance%20minister%20Palanivel%20Thiaga%20Rajan%20to%20cancel%20the%20Kattupalli%20port%20expansion%20project%20on%20the%20grounds%20that%20it%20would%20be%20a%20financial%20loss%20for%20the%20state.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20saddled%20with%20a%20white%20elephant%E2%80%9D%2C%20they%20wrote%2C%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EImpacts%20on%20people%2C%20environment%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20port%20expansion%20is%20the%20environmental%20degradation%20that%20the%20dredging%20for%20the%20project%20will%20cause%20in%20Pulicat%20Lake%3B%20the%20industrial%20pollution%20once%20it%20becomes%20operational%20is%20also%20a%20problem%2C%20experts%20have%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F20221251%2F32367057760_74358ff30a_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F20221251%2F32367057760_74358ff30a_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F20221251%2F32367057760_74358ff30a_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPulicat%20Lake.%20Photo%3A%20India%20Water%20Portal%2FFlickr.%20CC%20BY-NC%20SA%202.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPulicat%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20brackish%20water%20body%20and%20supports%20a%20huge%20diversity%20of%20birds%2C%20fish%20and%20other%20invertebrates.%20Several%20local%20fisher%20communities%20depend%20on%20the%20fishing%20resources%20that%20the%20Lake%20provides%20for%20their%20daily%20survival%20and%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKattupalli%20Island%2C%20a%20thin%20strip%20of%20land%20parallel%20to%20the%20coastline%2C%20functions%20as%20a%20barrier%20between%20Pulicat%20Lake%20and%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%20The%20barrier%20island%20is%20already%20facing%20erosion%20due%20to%20the%20Kattupalli%20port%20which%20is%20in%20operation.%20An%20expansion%20project%20here%20would%20cause%20further%20erosion%20of%20the%20island%2C%20experts%20have%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20island%20disappears%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20barrier%20between%20Pulicat%20Lake%20and%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%2C%20which%20will%20result%20in%20the%20death%20of%20the%20brackish%20water%20lake.%20This%20also%20means%20that%20the%20ocean%20will%20now%20be%20closer%20to%20Chennai%20city%20and%20the%20coast%20nearby%2C%20making%20the%20area%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20cyclones%2C%20sea%20level%20rise%20and%20storm%20surges%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20island%2C%20the%20loss%20of%20freshwater%20reserves%20immediately%20below%20it%20%E2%80%93%20that%20serve%20as%20a%20border%20security%20force%20to%20prevent%20saltwater%20intrusion%20into%20coastal%20freshwater%20aquifers%20on%20the%20mainland%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20a%20huge%20concern%2C%20Jayaraman%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGroundwater%20will%20become%20unusable%20and%20that%20will%20be%20a%20disaster%20of%20unimaginable%20magnitude%20because%20Tamil%20Nadu%20depends%20entirely%20on%20ground%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20we%20only%20celebrate%20infrastructure%20that%20is%20contracted%20with%20large%20amounts%20of%20money%20and%20tend%20to%20ignore%20the%20silent%20and%20invisible%20natural%20infrastructure%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20such%20as%20the%20Kattupalli%20Island%20and%20the%20functions%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20Tiruvallur%20district%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20security%20hinges%20on%20what%20we%20do%2C%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20done%20and%20what%20we%E2%80%99re%20doing%20in%20the%20Ennore-Pulicat%20wetland%20and%20Kattupalli%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgricultural%20security%20will%20also%20be%20at%20risk%20due%20to%20the%20project%2C%20because%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20agricultural%20areas%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20include%20Tiruvallur%2C%20Kancheepuram%2C%20Nagapattinam%20and%20Chengalpattu%20districts%2C%20which%20are%20along%20the%20coast%2C%20Jayaraman%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20protest%20by%20people%20against%20the%20port%20expansion%20is%20not%20a%20protest%20against%20development%2C%20commented%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20not%20opposed%20to%20infrastructure%20but%20are%20protecting%20the%20infrastructure%20that%20really%20matters%20to%20Chennai%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20infrastructure%20that%20the%20government%20is%20proposing%20here%20is%20different%20%E2%80%A6%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20big%2C%20the%20elite%2C%20for%20commerce%E2%80%A6it%20is%20not%20the%20infrastructure%20for%20survival.%20Nobody%20will%20oppose%20a%20road%20to%20the%20market%2C%20or%20a%20basic%20hospital.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20more%20urgent%20infrastructure%20needs%20in%20the%20area%20than%20a%20port%20expansion%20that%20will%20be%20detrimental%20to%20people%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692596137000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F11151940%2Fkattupalli-village.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Factivists-request-tn-cm-stalin-to-scrap-kattupalli-port-expansion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20early%20August%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20had%20scheduled%20the%20public%20hearing%20for%20the%20project%20on%20September%205.%20It%20currently%20stands%20postponed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Factivists-request-tn-cm-stalin-to-scrap-kattupalli-port-expansion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%3A%20India's%20lunar%20lander%20Vikram%20searches%20for%20safe%20Moon%20landing%20spot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692596005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F11A3F%2Fproduction%2F_130855227_f4bk_kybgaaocfa.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66567437%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Day%20after%20Luna-25%20crash%2C%20India%20space%20agency%20says%20lander%20trying%20to%20find%20area%20without%20boulders%20or%20deep%20trenches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A302%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66567437%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66567437.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66567437.amp%22%7D%2