i%20says%20he%20waited%20for%20Arkan%20till%2011.30%20pm%20before%20he%20got%20worried%20and%20called%20him%20on%20his%20mobile.%20Arkan%20informed%20him%20that%20he%20had%20picked%20up%20the%20money%20and%20was%20on%20his%20way%20home.%20Then%20at%2011%3A45%20pm%2C%20Qureshi%20says%20in%20his%20police%20complaint%2C%20he%20received%20a%20call%20from%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20mobile%20phone%20but%20some%20unknown%20person%20spoke%20to%20him.%20The%20person%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20phone%20identified%20himself%20as%20a%20policeman%20and%20asked%20Qureshi%20to%20quickly%20reach%20the%20spot%20with%20Rs%2050%2C000%20or%20his%20son%20would%20be%20booked%20on%20charges%20of%20cow%20slaughter%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmere-possession-and-transportation-of-cattle-not-offence-under-up-cow-slaughter-law-allahabad-hc%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mere%20Possession%20and%20Transportation%20of%20Cattle%20Not%20Offence%20Under%20UP%20Cow%20Slaughter%20Law%E2%80%99%3A%20Allahabad%20HC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQureshi%20was%20rattled%20by%20this%20and%20he%20quickly%20summoned%20other%20locals%20and%20rushed%20to%20the%20Bilal%20Masjid%20area%20in%20the%20Cantonment%20area%20of%20Bareilly.%20He%20alleged%20he%20saw%20the%20police%20inspector%2C%20constables%20and%20the%20home%20guard%20brutally%20thrashing%20his%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20blood%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Qureshi%2C%20mentioning%20that%20there%20was%20a%20white%20car%20and%20a%20motorcycle%20parked%20at%20the%20spot.%20According%20to%20Qureshi%2C%20the%20SHO%20Chaubey%20reached%20the%20spot%20with%20his%20team%20after%20the%20village%20Pradhan%20called%20him%20on%20his%20phone.%20However%2C%20Qureshi%20alleged%2C%20the%20SHO%20defended%20the%20policemen%20and%20threatened%20to%20set%20their%20village%20on%20fire%20and%20shoot%20them%20if%20they%20kept%20on%20arguing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20application%20filed%20under%20CrPC%20156%20(3)%20in%20the%20local%20court%20on%20May%204%2C%20Qureshi%20submitted%20a%20video%20which%20he%20says%20was%20shot%20by%20locals%20and%20shows%20the%20police%20officer%20allegedly%20threatening%20them.%20He%20alleged%20his%20son%20had%20died%20due%20to%20the%20beating%20and%20accused%20the%20SHO%20of%20conspiracy.%20While%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20had%20alleged%20that%20he%20died%20of%20a%20head%20injury%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20or%20confirmation%20on%20the%20actual%20nature%20of%20the%20injury%20or%20the%20exact%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20autopsy%20report%20showed%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9C16%20injuries%E2%80%9D%20on%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20said%20Qureshi.%20However%2C%20despite%20submitting%20written%20complaints%20to%20the%20top%20officers%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20including%20the%20Bareilly%20senior%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20the%20inspector%20general%20and%20the%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%2C%20no%20FIR%20was%20registered%2C%20he%20said.%20Instead%2C%20he%20says%2C%20police%20filed%20a%20false%20case%20against%20him%20and%20other%20villagers%20for%20assaulting%20the%20team%20at%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20of%20the%20villagers%20and%20on%20April%2018%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20Arkan%20had%20died%20in%20a%20bike%20accident.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20people%20who%20live%20in%20the%20locality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bareilly%20police%20said%20then%2C%20adding%20that%20false%20information%20and%20rumours%20were%20being%20spread%20on%20social%20media%20about%20the%20manner%20of%20the%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20involved%20an%20enraged%20mob%20turning%20upon%20the%20police%20team%2C%20then%20Bareilly%20senior%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Prabhakar%20Chaudhary%20in%20a%20video%20statement%20said%20that%20police%20had%20reached%20the%20spot%20after%20locals%20informed%20them%20that%20there%20had%20been%20an%20accident.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20mischievous%20elements%20of%20the%20village%20reached%20the%20site%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20had%20shot%20him.%20Whereas%20the%20incident%20was%20purely%20an%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaudhary%20had%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalbir%20Singh%2C%20station%20house%20officer%20of%20Cantonment%20police%20station%2C%20where%20the%20FIR%20was%20lodged%2C%20confirmed%20that%20the%20FIR%20had%20been%20lodged%20and%20the%20matter%20was%20under%20investigation.%20He%20said%20the%20police%20had%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20the%20death%20was%20an%20accident.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20the%20evidence.%20It%20was%20an%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20added%20that%20three%20policemen%20had%20been%20injured%20after%20the%20angry%20mob%20had%20assaulted%20them%20after%20Arkan%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20reporters%20from%20his%20hospital%20bed%2C%20an%20injured%20sub-inspector%20Dharmendra%20Kumar%20had%20said%20that%20the%20mob%20even%20tried%20to%20snatch%20his%20official%20pistol.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692595662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F11160124%2Fup_police_1200x768.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-muslim-teenager-cow-slaughter-death%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bareilly%20police%20had%20maintained%20that%20the%20teenager%2C%20Arkan%20Ali%2C%20had%20died%20in%20an%20accident.%20His%20father%20has%20alleged%20that%20police%20had%20threatened%20to%20register%20a%20'cow%20slaughter'%20case%20against%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Futtar-pradesh-police-muslim-teenager-cow-slaughter-death%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%