it-to-manipur-killings%2Farticleshow%2F102881254.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20of%20the%20three%20Kuki%20people%20in%20Ukhrul%20is%20the%20first%20attack%20in%20the%20region%20of%20the%20state%20which%20has%20been%20roiled%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20May.%20Over%20150%20people%20have%20died%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20geography%20is%20now%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fthree-kuki-people-killed-in-fresh-violence-in-manipur%5C%22%3Eidentified%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Thangkhokai%20Haokip%2C%20Jamkhogin%20Haokip%20and%20Hollenson%20Baite%2C%20were%20killed%20at%20around%204%3A30%20am%20on%20August%2018%20at%20the%20village%20of%20Thowai%20Kuki.%20Police%20said%20they%20had%20been%20designated%20as%20village%20guards%20by%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSCN-IM%20has%20identified%20the%20attack%20as%20something%20that%20took%20place%20%E2%80%9Cwithin%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Nagalim.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20said%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20on%20August%2020%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9CNagas%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20sectarian%20violence%20spilling%20into%20their%20areas%20under%20any%20circumstance%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSCN-IM%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Meitei%20separatist%20group%20Kanglei%20Yawol%20Kanna%20Lup%20(KYKL)%20and%20a%20Naga%20outfit%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20killings.%20The%20latter%2C%20it%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cdoesn%E2%80%99t%20represent%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20interest%20and%20welfare%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KYKL%20has%20said%20that%20it%20has%20no%20connection%20to%20the%20killings%20of%20the%20three%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlockade%20on%20NH2%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3C