80%99%20(%E2%80%98Hail%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20gathering%20occurred%20because%20inside%20the%20police%20station%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Christian%20community%20had%20been%20attempting%20to%20file%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20the%20group%20since%20noon%20on%20Sunday%20(August%2020).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20alleged%20that%20they%20had%20been%20assaulted%20with%20sticks%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20while%20praying.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20Sunday%2C%20when%20we%20gather%20to%20pray%20in%20church%2C%20we%20do%20so%20in%20fear%20%E2%80%93%20the%20fear%20of%20being%20attacked%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20anonymous%20Christian%20man.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20members%20from%20the%20group%20were%20also%20present%20inside%20the%20police%20station%2C%20where%20they%20continued%20to%20chant%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%2010%3A30%20or%2011%20am%2C%20people%20were%20praying%20inside%20the%20Siyyon%20Prathna%20Bhawan%20in%20the%20Tahirpur%20area%20when%20suddenly%2C%20a%20few%20individuals%20holding%20speakers%20entered%20the%20Bhawan.%20The%20speakers%20blared%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHindu%20rashtra%20banayenge%2C%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%20(Hindi%20for%20%E2%80%98We%20will%20make%20a%20Hindu%20nation%2C%20hail%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShivam%2C%20who%20was%20an%20eyewitness%20present%20during%20the%20prayer%2C%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20entered%20the%20Bhawan%20without%20permission%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20stop%20the%20prayer%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20country%20had%20changed%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eye%20desh%20dharm%20nirpeksh%20nahi%20raha%20hai%2C%20yaha%20ab%20kanoon%20badal%20gaya%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%2C%E2%80%9D%20meaning%20that%20the%20country%20is%20no%20longer%20secular%2C%20and%20the%20rules%20have%20changed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShivam%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20persons%20who%20reached%20the%20police%20station%20for%20help.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20from%20the%20Christian%20community%20have%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20mob%20which%20entered%20the%20Bhawan%20without%20permission%20was%20armed%20with%20swords%20and%20sticks%2C%20and%20that%20they%20also%20tore%20up%20Bibles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindi-urdu-hindutva-ram-temple-ayodhya-uttar-pradesh%5C%22%3EHindi-Hindu%20Nationalism%20and%20Secular%20Retreat%20in%20the%20Heartland%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShivam%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20attacked%20us%20with%20sticks%2C%20and%20many%20people%20were%20injured.%E2%80%9D%20This%20included%20several%20women%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20is%20Shivam%E2%80%99s%20sister%2C%20who%20suffered%20a%20muscle%20injury.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20women%20who%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20reveal%20their%20identities%20have%20claimed%20that%20they%20were%20beaten%20by%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20group%20and%20that%20its%20members%20attempted%20to%20remove%20their%20clothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20obtained%20access%20to%20a%20video%20of%20the%20church%20showing%20extensive%20damage%20inside%20the%20building%2C%20including%20the%20destruction%20of%20Bibles%20and%20images%20of%20Jesus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20interviewed%20the%20crowd%20that%20was%20shouting%20religious%20slogans%20outside%20the%20police%20station.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20were%20they%20praying%20in%20a%20Hindu-majority%20area%3F%20Our%20festival%2C%20Rakshabandhan%2C%20is%20coming%20up%20in%20a%20few%20days%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20conversion%20prayers%20in%20our%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Anmol%2C%20an%20RSS%20worker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELater%2C%20the%20group%20started%20shouting%2C%20claiming%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20attacked%20us%20first%2C%20and%20they%20were%20attempting%20conversions%2C%20which%20we%20won%E2%80%99t%20allow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Pastor%20Satpal%20Bhati%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20I%20say%3F%20When%20people%20in%20this%20country%20are%20not%20safe%20in%20their%20own%20land%2C%20there%20is%20no%20situation%20left%20to%20survive%20in.%20We%20have%20been%20praying%20here%20for%2013%20years%2C%20and%20I%20have%20never%20encountered%20a%20situation%20like%20the%20one%20we%20faced%20today.%20The%20Christian%20community%20lives%20in%20constant%20fear%2C%20fearing%20for%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20an%20FIR%20has%20not%20been%20registered%20in%20this%20matter%2C%20and%20the%20community%20has%20been%20attempting%20to%20file%20one%20since%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20report%20published%20by%20the%20United%20Christian%20Forum%20(UCF)%20reveals%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20attacks%20on%20Christians%20since%202014.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20their%20report%2C%20there%20were%20147%20attacks%20on%20churches%20in%202014%2C%20and%20this%20number%20has%20continued%20to%20rise%20almost%20every%20year.%20Last%20year%20saw%20599%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20and%20the%20first%20190%20days%20of%202023%20recorded%20400%20attacks%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Siasat%20Daily%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siasat.com%2F400-anti-christian-violence-incidents-in-india-in-first-half-of-2023-report-2638378%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCF%20report%20also%20indicates%20that%20violence%20against%20Christians%20has%20occurred%20in%2023%20states%20in%202023%2C%20with%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20leading%20with%20155%20incidents%2C%20followed%20by%20Chhattisgarh%20with%2084%20incidents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%20has%20been%20anxious%20to%20flaunt%20India%20as%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98mother%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20and%20mine%20the%20G20%20summit%20and%20events%20related%20to%20it%20to%20garner%20domestic%20political%20advantage%20before%20the%202024%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20its%20failure%20to%20control%20violence%20against%20the%20ethnic%20minority%20Kuki%20community%20in%20Manipur%20and%20against%20Muslims%20in%20Mewat%2C%20such%20attacks%20on%20minority%20places%20of%20worship%20are%20likely%20to%20highlight%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20inability%20or%20unwillingness%20to%20control%20such%20incidents%20even%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fharyana-violence-g20-summit-and-delhi-dog-relocations%5C%22%3Eglobal%20attention%20being%20on%20Delhi%20because%20of%20the%20forthcoming%20G20%20summit%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20rotational%20presidency%2C%20such%20incidents%20assume%20greater%20significance%20in%20bringing%20attention%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20record%20on%20democratic%20backsliding%20and%20ill-treatment%20of%20religious%C2%A0minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20at%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Jantar%20Mantar%20Road%2C%20Hindu%20Sena%20president%20Vishnu%20Gupta%20said%20at%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emahapanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20organised%20to%20protest%20the%20Nuh%20violence%20that%20India%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20divided%20in%201947%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20%5Bbut%5D%20as%20long%20as%20a%20single%20Muslim%20is%20living%20in%20this%20country%2C%20the%20partition%20will%20remain%20incomplete%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Faug%2F20%2Fnew-delhi-hate-speech-erupts-at-hindu-mahapanchayat-in-jantar-mantar-police-step-in-and-call-a-hal-2607141.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692559467000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21004747%2FGTB-Nagar.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchristians-attacked-in-delhi-church-during-sunday-service%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20100-strong%20mob%20surrounded%20the%20police%20station%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20GTB%20Nagar%20for%20several%20hours%20and%20raised%20provocative%20slogans%20as%20the%20pastor%20and%20injured%20persons%20reached%20to%20file%20their%C2%A0complaint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A189%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fchristians-attacked-in-delhi-church-during-sunday-service%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20president%20denies%20signing%20amended%20laws%20used%20against%20Imran%2C%20ex-minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692557513000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102881036%2Cimgsize-15576.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-president-denies-signing-amended-laws-used-against-imran-ex-minister%2Farticleshow%2F102881016.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102881016.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUsing%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20President%20Alvi%20refuted%20his%20involvement%20in%20approving%20th