Foutrage-as-jk-police-arrest-kashmir-walla-editor-for-reporting-on-pulwama-gun-battle%5C%22%3Eover%20the%20reporting%20of%20a%20gunfight%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20south%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Pulwama%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20has%20reported%20extensively%20on%20Kashmir%20for%20national%20and%20international%20publications%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%204%2C%20three%20days%20after%20he%20was%20questioned%20by%20police%20along%20with%20three%20more%20journalists%20for%20%E2%80%9Cincorrect%20reporting%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20gun%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZahid%20Wani%2C%20a%20top%20commander%20in%20the%20Pakistan-based%20Jaish-e-Mohammad%20outfit%2C%20was%20gunned%20down%20along%20with%20his%20three%20alleged%20associates%20%E2%80%93%20Kafeel%20Bhari%20alias%20Chotu%2C%20a%20suspected%20Pakistani%20militant%3B%20Waheed%20Ahmad%20Reshi%2C%20a%20local%20militant%3B%20and%20Inayat%20Ahmad%20Mir%2C%20son%20of%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20house%20where%20the%20encounter%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20claimed%20that%20Inayat%20had%20joined%20the%20militants%20%E2%80%9Crecently%E2%80%9D%2C%20his%20family%20initially%20rejected%20the%20police%20version.%20They%20also%20held%20a%20protest%20in%20Srinagar%20to%20demand%20the%20body%20of%20Inayat%2C%20who%20they%20said%20was%20%E2%80%9Cinnocent%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20police%20version%20and%20the%20claims%20of%20Inayat%E2%80%99s%20family%20were%20reported%20by%20sections%20of%20local%20media%20and%20the%20reports%20were%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Inayat%E2%80%99s%20sister%20later%20retracted%20her%20family%E2%80%99s%20claims%20during%20questioning%20by%20police%2C%20following%20which%20a%20case%20was%20filed%20against%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20as%20a%20blog%20by%20Shah%20more%20than%2012%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20saga%20of%20his%20revolving%20door%20arrests.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20be%20arrested%20five%20times%20within%20four%20months.%20Three%20FIRs%20under%20the%20stringent%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20and%20one%20%5Bunder%20the%5D%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20outlet%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fall-is-not-well-in-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%3EAll%20Is%20Not%20Well%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20past%2018%20months%2C%20%E2%80%A6%20we%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20a%20horrifying%20nightmare%20with%20the%20arrest%20and%20imprisonment%20of%20our%20founder-editor%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20the%20harassment%20of%20our%20reporters%20and%20staff%2C%20amid%20an%20already%20inhospitable%20climate%20for%20journalism%20in%20the%20region.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20(SIA)%20that%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20exclusively%20probe%20terrorism%20cases%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20raided%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20office%20as%20well%20as%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20Srinagar%20residence%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseditious%E2%80%9D%20opinion%20piece%20authored%20by%20a%20Kashmir%20University%20scholar%2C%20Alaa%20Fazili%2C%20which%20was%20published%20by%20the%20outlet%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFazili%20has%20also%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20and%20is%20languishing%20in%20a%20Jammu%20jail%20since%20last%20year.%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%20in%20this%20case%20is%20coming%20up%20for%20hearing%20before%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20on%20August%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20raid%2C%20most%20of%20our%20gadgets%20were%20seized%2C%20reporters%20were%20interrogated%2C%20and%20all%20documents%20were%20scrutinised.%20Since%20then%2C%20our%20interim%20editor%20has%20been%20summoned%20and%20questioned%20by%20the%20SIA%20multiple%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20outlet%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20booked%20Shah%20over%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20coverage%20of%20an%20encounter%20in%20Srinagar%20city%20on%20May%2019%2C%202020%2C%20during%20which%20over%20a%20dozen%20houses%20were%20razed%20to%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20had%20accused%20the%20security%20forces%20of%20looting%20cash%20and%20jewellery%20before%20setting%20their%20houses%20on%20fire%2C%20a%20charge%20denied%20by%20officials.%20Shah%20has%20got%20bail%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20case%2C%20in%20which%20Shah%20also%20got%20bail%20last%20year%2C%20was%20filed%20in%20Shopian%20on%20January%2030%2C%202021%20after%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Army%20was%20%E2%80%9Cpressuring%E2%80%9D%20the%20management%20of%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Shopian%2C%20then%20a%20hotbed%20of%20militancy%2C%20to%20organise%20the%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20denied%20the%20charge%20and%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20police%2C%20following%20which%20a%20case%20was%20filed.%20A%20court%20has%20granted%20bail%20to%20Shah%20in%20this%20case%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692556896000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F21000804%2FUntitled-design-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fthe-kashmir-walla-staff-say-website-social-media-blocked%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20statement%2C%20The%20Kashmir%20Walla%20staff%20said%20they%20have%20also%20received%20an%20eviction%20notice%20from%20the%20landlord%20of%20their%20office%20in%20Srinagar.%20The%20publication