has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20I%20took%20a%20stand%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20farmer%20family%20in%20rural%20Gwalior%2C%20Abhishek%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20teaching%20underprivileged%20children%20during%20his%20college%20days.%20In%202013%2C%20while%20studying%20engineering%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20he%20started%20devoting%20his%20weekends%20to%20teaching%20children%20in%20government-run%20shelter%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20classmates%20going%20to%20teach%20students%20in%20shelter%20homes.%20I%20went%20along%20with%20her%20and%20saw%20how%20such%20children%20are%20deprived%20of%20education.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20children%20of%20single%20parents%20and%20from%20tribal%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Coming%20from%20a%20rural%20background%2C%20I%20started%20connecting%20with%20them%20and%20I%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20teach%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20years%2C%20they%20formed%20a%20group%20of%20200%20volunteers%20and%20expanded%20their%20reach%20to%20Bhopal%20and%20Indore%20as%20well.%20By%20now%2C%20this%20was%20no%20more%20a%20weekend%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20NGO%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20lakh%20students%20and%20is%20making%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-2-1692363870-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327624%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20NGO%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20lakh%20students%20and%20is%20making%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%20after%20he%20graduated%2C%20Abhishek%20wanted%20to%20completely%20dedicate%20himself%20to%20teaching%20children.%20The%20decision%20was%20not%20welcomed%20by%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%2C%20who%20is%20a%20government%20officer%2C%20was%20completely%20against%20the%20decision.%20He%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20a%20good%20job%20and%20drop%20the%20idea.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20quit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20in%20a%20government%20school%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20ignore%20the%20challenges%20he%20needed%20to%20address.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20idea%20was%20to%20improve%20the%20learning%20experience%20of%20children%20so%20that%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20classrooms%2C%20their%20interest%20increases%20and%20they%20come%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20We%20already%20know%20that%20the%20dropout%20rate%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20challenges%20faced%20by%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20in%20the%20government%20school%20because%20when%20they%20are%20educated%20there%20in%20a%20better%20way%20they%20would%20not%20require%20tutoring.%20But%20my%20father%20was%20so%20angry%20at%20my%20decision%20that%20he%20stopped%20speaking%20to%20me.%20If%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20bedroom%2C%20he%20would%20move%20to%20the%20drawing-room%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20continued%20for%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20no%20one%20should%20quit%20on%20their%20dreams.%20Dreams%20have%20the%20power%20to%20become%20reality.%20This%20kept%20me%20motivated%20when%20my%20father%20did%20not%20speak%20to%20me.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20took%20a%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20today%2C%20he%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20I%20do.%20In%202019%2C%20when%20we%20invited%20former%20vice%20president%20M%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%20for%20a%20project%20launch%2C%20my%20father%20also%20joined%20us%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20He%20understood%20that%20I%20was%20serious%20about%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-3-1692363917-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327625%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20the%20govt%20school%20ecosystem%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20launching%20the%20non-profit%2C%20Abhishek%20started%20his%20journey%20with%20a%20government%20school%20for%20girls.%20Talking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%20in%202017%2C%20there%20were%20only%2079%20girls%20enrolled%20in%20the%20school.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20with%20the%20school%20to%20transform%20the%20education%20system%20with%20digital%20learning%20methods%2C%20the%20enrollment%20of%20girls%20increased%20to%20129.%20This%20impact%20encouraged%20us%20to%20understand%20that%20what%20we%20are%20doing%20is%20meaningful%20for%20the%20children%20in%20the%20government%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20kick%20off%20the%20work%2C%20Abhishek%E2%80%99s%20Muskaan%20Dreams%20signs%20an%20MoU%20(Memorandum%20of%20Understanding)%20with%20the%20state%20governments%20for%20a%20particular%20period.%20Thereafter%2C%20they%20conduct%20in-person%20meetings%20with%20district%20collectors%20who%20help%20them%20select%20government%20schools%20in%20rural%20areas%20based%20on%20the%20power%20availability%20to%20run%20the%20electronic%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20arrange%20meetings%20with%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20engage%20them%20in%20discussions%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20opportunities%20that%20lie%20ahead.%20It%20helps%20build%20enthusiasm%20and%20commitment%20among%20teachers%20and%20students%20and%20ensure%20their%20active%20involvement%20in%20the%20implementation%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collaborating%20with%20schools%2C%20we%20provide%20them%20with%20electronic%20devices%2C%20content%2C%20and%20training%20to%20teachers.%20We%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20performance%20of%20children%20in%20Maths%20and%20Science%20because%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20subject%20teachers%20in%20the%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fg0HA2PbezIc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20Dreams%20also%20uses%20a%20third%20party%20Tic%20Tac%20Learning%20app%E2%80%99s%20unique%20%E2%80%9Ctic-tac%E2%80%9D%20learning%20module%2C%20wherein%20they%20animate%20pictures%20and%20high-quality%20video%20content%20aligned%20with%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus.%20With%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20subjects%20like%20Science%20and%20Math%2C%20all%20chapters%20and%20exercises%20are%20converted%20into%20animated%20videos%20in%20Hindi.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20chapter%20on%20nutrients%20and%20food%20is%20converted%20into%20an%20animated%20video%20to%20disseminate%20information%20in%20an%20interesting%20and%20engaging%20way%2C%20and%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20story%20to%20help%20students%20retain%20what%20they%20learned%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20teacher%20training%20and%201-1%20feedback%20and%20support%20to%20teachers%20to%20ensure%20the%20adoption%20of%20technology%20in%20teaching%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20is%20divided%20into%20four%20modules%20that%20are%20mandatory%20for%20each%20teacher%20to%20attend.%20We%20make%20our%20teachers%20familiar%20with%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20digital%20lesson%2C%20teaching%2C%20and%20learning%20models%20using%20technology%20and%20methods%20of%20delivering%20instruction.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20invest%20in%20teacher%20training%20to%20foster%20a%20stronger%20education%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20informs%20that%20his%20team%20works%20with%20any%20school%20for%202-3%20years.%20After%20they%20leave%2C%20they%20provide%20virtual%20tech%20support%20to%20ensure%20teachers%20are%20ensuring%20the%20consistency%20of%20digital%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20we%20stop%20hand%20holding%20the%20schools%2C%20we%20try%20to%20build%20capacity%20to%20lower%20dependency%20on%20our%20team%20so%20they%20remain%20efficient%20post-exit.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20we%20have%20engaged%20private%20organisations%20like%20Pernod%20Ricard%20India%20Foundation%2C%20LTI%20Mindtree%2C%20Yash%20Technologies%2C%20and%20Acuity%20Knowledge%20Partners%20who%20offer%20resources%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20funding%20to%20support%20the%20sustainability%20of%20our%20initiative%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%981%20Million%20by%202025%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20says%20that%20every%20year%2C%20they%20conduct%20an%20annual%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20experience%20of%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F105260%2Findia-literacy-project-interactive-learning-rural-government-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.