ya%20Sethu%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Muskaan%20Dreams%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692365151000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D327615%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abhishek%20Dubey%20runs%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20a%20non-profit%20that%20aims%20to%20transform%20government%20school%20classrooms%20into%20digital%20hubs%20combining%20technology%20with%20fun%20ways%20to%20learn.%20He%20narrates%20why%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20do%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327615%2Fengineer-animates-ncert-syllabus-turns-govt-schools-into-digital-classrooms-muskaan-dreams%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20Ways%20to%20Read%20Food%20Labels%3A%20Health%20Coach%20Shares%20Unseen%20Risks%20in%20Everyday%20Food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERemember%20those%20small%20discs%20called%20%E2%80%98tazos%E2%80%99%20we%20found%20inside%20chips%20packets%20in%20the%202000s%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20a%20worldwide%20promotional%20campaign%20created%20first%20by%20the%20brand%20Frito-Lay%20in%201994%2C%20they%20were%20such%20a%20rage%20in%20schools%20as%20well.%20Everyone%20would%20discuss%2C%20swap%2C%20share%2C%20gloat%20about%20the%20latest%20Tazos%20they%20had%20managed%20to%20collect%20with%20their%20friends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20ever%20think%20of%20how%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312390%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-anish-malpani-makes-worlds-first-sunglasses-with-recycled-chips-packets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echips%20you%20consumed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20building%20your%20Tazo%20collection%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20bought%20seve