0MeenaBagh%20Farms%20(%40meenabaghfarms)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Shimla%20to%20Delhi%20and%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20any%20%3Cem%3Epahadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20native%20will%20tell%20you%2C%20the%20draw%20of%20a%20fancy%20city%20life%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20homeliness%20of%20the%20hills.%20This%20was%20the%20case%20with%20Sanjay%20too.%20A%20childhood%20spent%20in%20a%20boarding%20school%20in%20Shimla%20and%20summer%20vacations%20spent%20in%20his%20family%20orchards%20%E2%80%94%20were%20some%20of%20his%20fondest%20memories.%20He%20carried%20them%20with%20him%20even%20later%20on%20in%20life%20as%20he%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F284474%2Fhow-couple-quit-city-life-to-build-sustainable-homestay-in-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20travelled%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20journalist%20and%20writer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20in%20Delhi%20for%20work%2C%20Sanjay%20dearly%20missed%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20calm%20that%20came%20with%20them.%20Fast-paced%20city%20life%20was%20not%20his%20cup%20of%20tea%20%E2%80%94%20a%20realisation%20that%20dawned%20on%20him%20after%20spending%20a%20few%20years%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDelhi%20has%20a%20way%20of%20spitting%20you%20out%20after%20a%20while%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20figured.%20Today%20in%20retrospect%2C%20Sanjay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20people%20have%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324508%2Fbest-pet-friendly-homestays-across-india-travel-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoption%20of%20doing%20something%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20place%20where%20they%20hail%20from%2C%20they%20should.%20There%20is%20no%20point%20in%20moving%20into%20the%20city%20like%20the%20masses.%20You%20will%20only%20be%20adding%20t