3Cp%3EApart%20from%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20animals%20and%20giving%20them%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286180%2Fhow-to-make-animal-dog-bird-shelter-help-for-summer-diy-food-water-streets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20food%20and%20shelter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sai%20also%20works%20for%20their%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20check%20if%20the%20animal%20has%20been%20harassed%2C%20sexually%20molested%2C%20or%20was%20about%20to%20be%20slaughtered%20illegally.%20There%20are%20ways%20to%20fight%20against%20such%20atrocities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20years%2C%20Sai%20has%20been%20reporting%20cases%20of%20violence%20against%20animals%20to%20the%20local%20police.%20Many%20of%20them%20violate%20rules%20under%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Animal%20Preservation%20Act%2C%20IPC%20429%2C%20Prevention%20of%20Cruelty%20to%20Animals%20Act%2C%20and%20Food%20Safety%20and%20Standards%20Act%20(FSSA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20cases%20that%20are%20pending%20in%20lower%20courts%20including%20dog%20poisoning%2C%20cattle%20trafficking%20and%20animal%20abuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20also%20started%20sensitisation%20of%20police%20officers%20towards%20animal%20cruelty.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20conducting%20seminars%20in%202021%20and%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20nearly%202%2C000%20police%20offers.%20It%20is%20important%20because%20many%20officers%20in%20rural%20areas%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20against%20animal%20abuse%20and%20the%20correct%20measures%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%E2%80%99s%20inbox%20and%20phone%20are%20always%20buzzing%20with%20requests%20from%20people%20all%20around%20the%20city%20as%20well%20as%20the%20outskirts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThree%20years%20ago%2C%20we%20found%20a%20cow%20that%20had%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20and%20injured%20its%20leg.%20It%20was%20in%20deep%20pain%20and%20needed%20immediate%20attention.%20I%20had%20seen%20many%20of%20Sai%E2%80%99s%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20and%20was%20aware%20of%20his%20work.%20So%20I%20called%20for%20his%20help%2C%20and%20he%20rescued%20the%20cow%20and%20took%20it%20to%20his%20sanctuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kathir%20Selvan%20who%20has%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20Sai%20ever%20since.%20He%20now%20informs%20Sai%20of%20any%20animal%20in%20distress%20that%20he%20happens%20to%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20conducts%20sensitization%20seminars%20with%20the%20police%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai--1691586928-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESai%20also%20conducts%20seminars%20for%20the%20sensitisation%20of%20police%20officers%20towards%20animal%20cruelty%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Sai%20Vignesh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20motivations%20and%20reflecting%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20Sai%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20an%20animal%20in%20pain%2C%20it%20almost%20feels%20like%20I%20am%20experiencing%20it%20myself.%20They%20deserve%20to%20live%20as%20much%20as%20we%20do.%20There%20are%20days%20when%20the%20sanctuary%20is%20low%20on%20budget%20and%20hands%2C%20but%20we%20have%20somehow%20survived%20for%20all%20these%20years.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20when%20I%20look%20back%20and%20see%20nature%20thriving%20in%20all%20its%20glory%20at%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20it%20fills%20me%20with%20indescribable%20joy%20and%20satisfaction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20you%20can%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%2C%20who%20also%20works%20as%20a%20web%20developer%2C%20dedicates%20most%20of%20his%20income%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20the%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20my%20income%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20keep%20donating%20regularly%20in%20kind%20and%20money.%20The%20per-day%20expense%20for%20the%20sanctuary%E2%80%99s%20upkeep%20and%20for%20feeding%20the%20animals%20comes%20to%20around%20Rs%2018%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20who%20wants%20to%20contribute%20can%20do%20it%20in%20any%20form.%20You%20can%20volunteer%20here%20as%20we%20are%20always%20short%20of%20hands%2C%20or%20you%20can%20also%20donate%20money%2C%20food%2C%20or%20medicines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20regularly%20shares%20updates%20on%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20health%20and%20well-being%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Sai%20is%20planning%20to%20build%20a%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20the%20sanctuary%20for%20animals%20with%20contagious%20diseases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20further%20his%20cause%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20Sai%20at%2089393%2020846.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691645042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fsai-1-1691587222.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D326836%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sai%20Vignesh%20(22)%20started%20helping%20animals%20at%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20thanks%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20grandfather.%20Later%2C%20he%20started%20Almighty%20Animal%20Care%20Trust%20in%20Tiruvallur%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20provide%20a%20safe%20haven%20for%20animals.%20Currently%2C%20over%20250%20animals%20reside%20in%20his%20sanctuary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326836%2Fsai-vignesh-rescuer-activist-started-almighty-animal-care-trust-chennai%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Better%20India%20Among%20Top%204%20Finalists%20for%20Prestigious%20Social%20Entrepreneur%20of%20the%20Year%20Award%2C%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20Anuradha%20Kedia%20and%20Dhimant%20Parekh%20co-founded%20The%20Better%20India%20in%202009%2C%20it%20was%20with%20a%20simple%20aim%20%E2%80%94%20to%20show%20an%20underreported%20and%20underrepresented%20faction%20of%20news%2C%20one%20that%20could%20highlight%20the%20stories%20of%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312839%2Frevolutionary-indians-who-left-mark-in-art-science-history-photos%2F%5C%22%3Esilently%20brewing%20revolutions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Better%20India%20(TBI)%20has%20ushered%20a%20whole%20new%20positive%20movement%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20by%20using%20the%20power%20of%20stories%20to%20effect%20large-scale%20social%20impact.%20It%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20positive%20stories%20platform%20publishing%20in%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20Gujarati%2C%20Bangla%20%26amp%3B%20Marathi.%20It%20unearths%20stories%20of%20ordinary%20unsung%20heroes%2C%20community%20change-makers%2C%20remarkable%20ideas%20and%20ground-breaking%20innovations%20that%20often%20go%20unnoticed%20by%20traditional%20media.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20the%20growth%20over